var book = {
	"name": "Ezekiel",
	"numChapters": 48,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In my thirtieth year, in the fourth month on the fifth day, while I was among the exiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20466A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20466A\"></sup> by the Kebar River,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20466B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20466B\"></sup> the heavens were opened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20466C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20466C\"></sup> and I saw visions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20466D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20466D\"></sup> of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>On the fifth of the month—it was the fifth year of the exile of King Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20467E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20467E\"></sup>—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Ezekiel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20468F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20468F\"></sup> the priest, the son of Buzi, by the Kebar River in the land of the Babylonians. There the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was on him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20468G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20468G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I looked, and I saw a windstorm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20469H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20469H\"></sup> coming out of the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20469I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20469I\"></sup>—an immense cloud with flashing lightning and surrounded by brilliant light. The center of the fire looked like glowing metal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20469J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20469J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and in the fire was what looked like four living creatures.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20470K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20470K\"></sup> In appearance their form was human,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20470L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20470L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but each of them had four faces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20471M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20471M\"></sup> and four wings.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Their legs were straight; their feet were like those of a calf and gleamed like burnished bronze.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20472N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20472N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Under their wings on their four sides they had human hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20473O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20473O\"></sup> All four of them had faces and wings,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and the wings of one touched the wings of another. Each one went straight ahead; they did not turn as they moved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20474P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20474P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Their faces looked like this: Each of the four had the face of a human being, and on the right side each had the face of a lion, and on the left the face of an ox; each also had the face of an eagle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20475Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20475Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Such were their faces. They each had two wings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20476R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20476R\"></sup> spreading out upward, each wing touching that of the creature on either side; and each had two other wings covering its body.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Each one went straight ahead. Wherever the spirit would go, they would go, without turning as they went.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20477S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20477S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The appearance of the living creatures was like burning coals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20478T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20478T\"></sup> of fire or like torches. Fire moved back and forth among the creatures; it was bright, and lightning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20478U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20478U\"></sup> flashed out of it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The creatures sped back and forth like flashes of lightning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20479V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20479V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As I looked at the living creatures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20480W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20480W\"></sup> I saw a wheel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20480X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20480X\"></sup> on the ground beside each creature with its four faces.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This was the appearance and structure of the wheels: They sparkled like topaz,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20481Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20481Y\"></sup> and all four looked alike. Each appeared to be made like a wheel intersecting a wheel.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As they moved, they would go in any one of the four directions the creatures faced; the wheels did not change direction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20482Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20482Z\"></sup> as the creatures went.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Their rims were high and awesome, and all four rims were full of eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20483AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20483AA\"></sup> all around.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When the living creatures moved, the wheels beside them moved; and when the living creatures rose from the ground, the wheels also rose.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Wherever the spirit would go, they would go,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20485AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20485AB\"></sup> and the wheels would rise along with them, because the spirit of the living creatures was in the wheels.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When the creatures moved, they also moved; when the creatures stood still, they also stood still; and when the creatures rose from the ground, the wheels rose along with them, because the spirit of the living creatures was in the wheels.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20486AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20486AC\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Spread out above the heads of the living creatures was what looked something like a vault,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20487AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20487AD\"></sup> sparkling like crystal, and awesome.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Under the vault their wings were stretched out one toward the other, and each had two wings covering its body.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When the creatures moved, I heard the sound of their wings, like the roar of rushing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20489AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20489AE\"></sup> waters, like the voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20489AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20489AF\"></sup> of the Almighty, like the tumult of an army.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20489AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20489AG\"></sup> When they stood still, they lowered their wings.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Then there came a voice from above the vault over their heads as they stood with lowered wings.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Above the vault over their heads was what looked like a throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20491AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20491AH\"></sup> of lapis lazuli,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20491AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20491AI\"></sup> and high above on the throne was a figure like that of a man.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20491AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20491AJ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>I saw that from what appeared to be his waist up he looked like glowing metal, as if full of fire, and that from there down he looked like fire; and brilliant light surrounded him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20492AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20492AK\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Like the appearance of a rainbow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20493AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20493AL\"></sup> in the clouds on a rainy day, so was the radiance around him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20493AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20493AM\"></sup>This was the appearance of the likeness of the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20493AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20493AN\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. When I saw it, I fell facedown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20493AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20493AO\"></sup> and I heard the voice of one speaking."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>He said to me, “Son of man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20494A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20494A\"></sup> stand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20494B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20494B\"></sup> up on your feet and I will speak to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20494C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20494C\"></sup>”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>As he spoke, the Spirit came into me and raised me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20495D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20495D\"></sup> to my feet, and I heard him speaking to me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He said: “Son of man, I am sending you to the Israelites, to a rebellious nation that has rebelled against me; they and their ancestors have been in revolt against me to this very day.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20496E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20496E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The people to whom I am sending you are obstinate and stubborn.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20497F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20497F\"></sup> Say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20497G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20497G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And whether they listen or fail to listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20498H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20498H\"></sup>—for they are a rebellious people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20498I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20498I\"></sup>—they will know that a prophet has been among them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20498J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20498J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you, son of man, do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20499K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20499K\"></sup> of them or their words. Do not be afraid, though briers and thorns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20499L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20499L\"></sup> are all around you and you live among scorpions. Do not be afraid of what they say or be terrified by them, though they are a rebellious people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20499M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20499M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You must speak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20500N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20500N\"></sup> my words to them, whether they listen or fail to listen, for they are rebellious.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20500O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20500O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But you, son of man, listen to what I say to you. Do not rebel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20501P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20501P\"></sup> like that rebellious people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20501Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20501Q\"></sup> open your mouth and eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20501R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20501R\"></sup> what I give you.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I looked, and I saw a hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20502S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20502S\"></sup> stretched out to me. In it was a scroll,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20502T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20502T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>which he unrolled before me. On both sides of it were written words of lament and mourning and woe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20503U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20503U\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>And he said to me, “Son of man, eat what is before you, eat this scroll; then go and speak to the people of Israel.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I opened my mouth, and he gave me the scroll to eat.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then he said to me, “Son of man, eat this scroll I am giving you and fill your stomach with it.” So I ate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20506A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20506A\"></sup> it, and it tasted as sweet as honey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20506B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20506B\"></sup> in my mouth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He then said to me: “Son of man, go now to the people of Israel and speak my words to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20507C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20507C\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You are not being sent to a people of obscure speech and strange language,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20508D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20508D\"></sup> but to the people of Israel—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>not to many peoples of obscure speech and strange language, whose words you cannot understand. Surely if I had sent you to them, they would have listened to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20509E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20509E\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But the people of Israel are not willing to listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20510F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20510F\"></sup> to you because they are not willing to listen to me, for all the Israelites are hardened and obstinate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20510G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20510G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But I will make you as unyielding and hardened as they are.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20511H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20511H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make your forehead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20512I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20512I\"></sup> like the hardest stone, harder than flint.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20512J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20512J\"></sup> Do not be afraid of them or terrified by them, though they are a rebellious people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20512K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20512K\"></sup>”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he said to me, “Son of man, listen carefully and take to heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20513L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20513L\"></sup> all the words I speak to you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Go<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20514M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20514M\"></sup> now to your people in exile and speak to them. Say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20514N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20514N\"></sup> whether they listen or fail to listen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20514O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20514O\"></sup>”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the Spirit lifted me up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20515P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20515P\"></sup> and I heard behind me a loud rumbling sound as the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rose from the place where it was standing.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It was the sound of the wings of the living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20516Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20516Q\"></sup> brushing against each other and the sound of the wheels beside them, a loud rumbling sound.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20516R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20516R\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20517S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20517S\"></sup> then lifted me up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20517T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20517T\"></sup> and took me away, and I went in bitterness and in the anger of my spirit, with the strong hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20517U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20517U\"></sup> on me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I came to the exiles who lived at Tel Aviv near the Kebar River.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20518V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20518V\"></sup> And there, where they were living, I sat among them for seven days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20518W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20518W\"></sup>—deeply distressed.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>At the end of seven days the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20519X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20519X\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Son of man, I have made you a watchman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20520Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20520Y\"></sup> for the people of Israel; so hear the word I speak and give them warning from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20520Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20520Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When I say to a wicked person, ‘You will surely die,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20521AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20521AA\"></sup>’ and you do not warn them or speak out to dissuade them from their evil ways in order to save their life, that wicked person will die for their sin, and I will hold you accountable for their blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20521AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20521AB\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But if you do warn the wicked person and they do not turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20522AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20522AC\"></sup> from their wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20522AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20522AD\"></sup> or from their evil ways, they will die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20522AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20522AE\"></sup> for their sin; but you will have saved yourself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20522AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20522AF\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Again, when a righteous person turns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20523AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20523AG\"></sup> from their righteousness and does evil, and I put a stumbling block<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20523AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20523AH\"></sup> before them, they will die. Since you did not warn them, they will die for their sin. The righteous things that person did will not be remembered, and I will hold you accountable for their blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20523AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20523AI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But if you do warn the righteous person not to sin and they do not sin, they will surely live because they took warning, and you will have saved yourself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20524AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20524AJ\"></sup>”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20525AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20525AK\"></sup> was on me there, and he said to me, “Get up and go<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20525AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20525AL\"></sup> out to the plain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20525AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20525AM\"></sup> and there I will speak to you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So I got up and went out to the plain. And the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was standing there, like the glory I had seen by the Kebar River,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20526AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20526AN\"></sup> and I fell facedown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20526AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20526AO\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then the Spirit came into me and raised me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20527AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20527AP\"></sup> to my feet. He spoke to me and said: “Go, shut yourself inside your house.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20527AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20527AQ\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And you, son of man, they will tie with ropes; you will be bound so that you cannot go out among the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20528AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20528AR\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will make your tongue stick to the roof<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20529AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20529AS\"></sup> of your mouth so that you will be silent and unable to rebuke them, for they are a rebellious people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20529AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20529AT\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But when I speak to you, I will open your mouth and you shall say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20530AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20530AU\"></sup> Whoever will listen let them listen, and whoever will refuse let them refuse; for they are a rebellious people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20530AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20530AV\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>“Now, son of man, take a block of clay, put it in front of you and draw the city of Jerusalem on it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then lay siege to it: Erect siege works against it, build a ramp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20532A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20532A\"></sup> up to it, set up camps against it and put battering rams around it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20532B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20532B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then take an iron pan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20533C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20533C\"></sup> place it as an iron wall between you and the city and turn your face toward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20533D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20533D\"></sup> it. It will be under siege, and you shall besiege it. This will be a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20533E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20533E\"></sup> to the people of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20533F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20533F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Then lie on your left side and put the sin of the people of Israel upon yourself. You are to bear their sin for the number of days you lie on your side.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I have assigned you the same number of days as the years of their sin. So for 390 days you will bear the sin of the people of Israel.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“After you have finished this, lie down again, this time on your right side, and bear the sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20536G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20536G\"></sup> of the people of Judah. I have assigned you 40 days, a day for each year.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20536H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20536H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Turn your face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20537I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20537I\"></sup> toward the siege of Jerusalem and with bared arm prophesy against her.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will tie you up with ropes so that you cannot turn from one side to the other until you have finished the days of your siege.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20538J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20538J\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Take wheat and barley, beans and lentils, millet and spelt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20539K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20539K\"></sup> put them in a storage jar and use them to make bread for yourself. You are to eat it during the 390 days you lie on your side.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Weigh out twenty shekels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20540L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20540L\"></sup> of food to eat each day and eat it at set times.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Also measure out a sixth of a hin of water and drink it at set times.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20541M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20541M\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Eat the food as you would a loaf of barley bread; bake it in the sight of the people, using human excrement<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20542N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20542N\"></sup> for fuel.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “In this way the people of Israel will eat defiled food among the nations where I will drive them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20543O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20543O\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I said, “Not so, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20544P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20544P\"></sup> I have never defiled myself. From my youth until now I have never eaten anything found dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20544Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20544Q\"></sup> or torn by wild animals. No impure meat has ever entered my mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20544R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20544R\"></sup>”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Very well,” he said, “I will let you bake your bread over cow dung instead of human excrement.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He then said to me: “Son of man, I am about to cut off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20546S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20546S\"></sup> the food supply in Jerusalem. The people will eat rationed food in anxiety and drink rationed water in despair,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20546T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20546T\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>for food and water will be scarce.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20547U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20547U\"></sup> They will be appalled at the sight of each other and will waste away because of their sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20547V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20547V\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“Now, son of man, take a sharp sword and use it as a barber’s razor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20548A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20548A\"></sup> to shave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20548B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20548B\"></sup> your head and your beard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20548C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20548C\"></sup> Then take a set of scales and divide up the hair.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the days of your siege come to an end, burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20549D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20549D\"></sup> a third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20549E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20549E\"></sup> of the hair inside the city. Take a third and strike it with the sword all around the city. And scatter a third to the wind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20549F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20549F\"></sup> For I will pursue them with drawn sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20549G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20549G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But take a few hairs and tuck them away in the folds of your garment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20550H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20550H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Again, take a few of these and throw them into the fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20551I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20551I\"></sup> and burn them up. A fire will spread from there to all Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: This is Jerusalem, which I have set in the center of the nations, with countries all around her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20552J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20552J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Yet in her wickedness she has rebelled against my laws and decrees more than the nations and countries around her. She has rejected my laws and has not followed my decrees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20553K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20553K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You have been more unruly than the nations around you and have not followed my decrees or kept my laws. You have not even conformed to the standards of the nations around you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20554L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20554L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I myself am against you, Jerusalem, and I will inflict punishment on you in the sight of the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20555M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20555M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Because of all your detestable idols, I will do to you what I have never done before and will never do again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20556N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20556N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore in your midst parents will eat their children, and children will eat their parents.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20557O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20557O\"></sup> I will inflict punishment on you and will scatter all your survivors to the winds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20557P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20557P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore as surely as I live,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20558Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20558Q\"></sup> declares the Sovereign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20558R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20558R\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, because you have defiled my sanctuary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20558S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20558S\"></sup> with all your vile images<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20558T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20558T\"></sup> and detestable practices,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20558U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20558U\"></sup> I myself will shave you; I will not look on you with pity or spare you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20558V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20558V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A third of your people will die of the plague or perish by famine inside you; a third will fall by the sword outside your walls; and a third I will scatter to the winds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20559W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20559W\"></sup> and pursue with drawn sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20559X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20559X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Then my anger will cease and my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20560Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20560Y\"></sup> against them will subside, and I will be avenged.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20560Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20560Z\"></sup> And when I have spent my wrath on them, they will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken in my zeal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20560AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20560AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I will make you a ruin and a reproach among the nations around you, in the sight of all who pass by.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20561AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20561AB\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You will be a reproach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20562AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20562AC\"></sup> and a taunt, a warning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20562AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20562AD\"></sup> and an object of horror to the nations around you when I inflict punishment on you in anger and in wrath and with stinging rebuke.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20562AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20562AE\"></sup> I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20562AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20562AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When I shoot at you with my deadly and destructive arrows of famine, I will shoot to destroy you. I will bring more and more famine upon you and cut off your supply of food.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20563AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20563AG\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will send famine and wild beasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20564AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20564AH\"></sup> against you, and they will leave you childless. Plague and bloodshed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20564AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20564AI\"></sup> will sweep through you, and I will bring the sword against you. I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20564AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20564AJ\"></sup>”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20566A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20566A\"></sup> against the mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20566B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20566B\"></sup> of Israel; prophesy against them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20566C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20566C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say: ‘You mountains of Israel, hear the word of the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to the mountains and hills, to the ravines and valleys:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20567D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20567D\"></sup> I am about to bring a sword against you, and I will destroy your high places.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20567E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20567E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your altars will be demolished and your incense altars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20568F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20568F\"></sup> will be smashed; and I will slay your people in front of your idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20568G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20568G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will lay the dead bodies of the Israelites in front of their idols, and I will scatter your bones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20569H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20569H\"></sup> around your altars.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20569I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20569I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Wherever you live,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20570J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20570J\"></sup> the towns will be laid waste and the high places<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20570K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20570K\"></sup> demolished, so that your altars will be laid waste and devastated, your idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20570L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20570L\"></sup> smashed and ruined, your incense altars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20570M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20570M\"></sup> broken down, and what you have made wiped out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20570N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20570N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your people will fall slain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20571O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20571O\"></sup> among you, and you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20571P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20571P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘But I will spare some, for some of you will escape<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20572Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20572Q\"></sup> the sword when you are scattered among the lands and nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20572R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20572R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then in the nations where they have been carried captive, those who escape will remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20573S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20573S\"></sup> me—how I have been grieved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20573T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20573T\"></sup> by their adulterous hearts, which have turned away from me, and by their eyes, which have lusted after their idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20573U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20573U\"></sup> They will loathe themselves for the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20573V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20573V\"></sup> they have done and for all their detestable practices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20573W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20573W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20574X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20574X\"></sup> I did not threaten in vain to bring this calamity on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20574Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20574Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Strike your hands together and stamp your feet and cry out “Alas!” because of all the wicked and detestable practices of the people of Israel, for they will fall by the sword, famine and plague.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20575Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20575Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>One who is far away will die of the plague, and one who is near will fall by the sword, and anyone who survives and is spared will die of famine. So will I pour out my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20576AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20576AA\"></sup> on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20576AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20576AB\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when their people lie slain among their idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20577AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20577AC\"></sup> around their altars, on every high hill and on all the mountaintops, under every spreading tree and every leafy oak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20577AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20577AD\"></sup>—places where they offered fragrant incense to all their idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20577AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20577AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And I will stretch out my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20578AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20578AF\"></sup> against them and make the land a desolate waste from the desert to Diblah—wherever they live. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20578AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20578AG\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to the land of Israel:“‘The end!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20580A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20580A\"></sup> The end has comeupon the four corners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20580B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20580B\"></sup> of the land!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The end is now upon you,and I will unleash my anger against you.I will judge you according to your conduct<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20581C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20581C\"></sup>and repay you for all your detestable practices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20581D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20581D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will not look on you with pity;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20582E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20582E\"></sup>I will not spare you.I will surely repay you for your conductand for the detestable practices among you.“‘Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20582F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20582F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Disaster!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20583G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20583G\"></sup> Unheard-of disaster!See, it comes!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The end<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20584H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20584H\"></sup> has come!The end has come!It has roused itself against you.See, it comes!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Doom has come upon you,upon you who dwell in the land.The time has come! The day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20585I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20585I\"></sup> is near!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20585J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20585J\"></sup>There is panic, not joy, on the mountains.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I am about to pour out my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20586K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20586K\"></sup> on youand spend my anger against you.I will judge you according to your conductand repay you for all your detestable practices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20586L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20586L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will not look on you with pity;I will not spare you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20587M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20587M\"></sup>I will repay you for your conductand for the detestable practices among you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20587N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20587N\"></sup>“‘Then you will know that it is I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who strikes you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20587O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20587O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘See, the day!See, it comes!Doom has burst forth,the rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20588P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20588P\"></sup> has budded,arrogance has blossomed!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20589Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20589Q\"></sup> has arisen,a rod to punish the wicked.None of the people will be left,none of that crowd—none of their wealth,nothing of value.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20589R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20589R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The time has come!The day has arrived!Let not the buyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20590S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20590S\"></sup> rejoicenor the seller grieve,for my wrath is on the whole crowd.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20590T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20590T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The seller will not recoverthe property that was sold—as long as both buyer and seller live.For the vision concerning the whole crowdwill not be reversed.Because of their sins, not one of themwill preserve their life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20591U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20591U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“‘They have blown the trumpet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20592V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20592V\"></sup>they have made all things ready,but no one will go into battle,for my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20592W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20592W\"></sup> is on the whole crowd.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Outside is the sword;inside are plague and famine.Those in the countrywill die by the sword;those in the citywill be devoured by famine and plague.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20593X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20593X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The fugitives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20594Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20594Y\"></sup> who escapewill flee to the mountains.Like doves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20594Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20594Z\"></sup> of the valleys,they will all moan,each for their own sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20594AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20594AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Every hand will go limp;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20595AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20595AB\"></sup>every leg will be wet with urine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20595AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20595AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They will put on sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20596AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20596AD\"></sup>and be clothed with terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20596AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20596AE\"></sup>Every face will be covered with shame,and every head will be shaved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20596AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20596AF\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“‘They will throw their silver into the streets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20597AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20597AG\"></sup>and their gold will be treated as a thing unclean.Their silver and goldwill not be able to deliver themin the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20597AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20597AH\"></sup>It will not satisfy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20597AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20597AI\"></sup> their hungeror fill their stomachs,for it has caused them to stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20597AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20597AJ\"></sup> into sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20597AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20597AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They took pride in their beautiful jewelryand used it to make<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20598AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20598AL\"></sup> their detestable idols.They made it into vile images;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20598AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20598AM\"></sup>therefore I will make it a thing unclean for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20598AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20598AN\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will give their wealth as plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20599AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20599AO\"></sup> to foreignersand as loot to the wicked of the earth,who will defile it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20599AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20599AP\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will turn my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20600AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20600AQ\"></sup> away from the people,and robbers will desecrate the place I treasure.They will enter itand will defile it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20600AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20600AR\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“‘Prepare chains!For the land is full of bloodshed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20601AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20601AS\"></sup>and the city is full of violence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20601AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20601AT\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I will bring the most wicked of nationsto take possession of their houses.I will put an end to the pride of the mighty,and their sanctuaries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20602AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20602AU\"></sup> will be desecrated.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20602AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20602AV\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When terror comes,they will seek peace in vain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20603AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20603AW\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Calamity upon calamity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20604AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20604AX\"></sup> will come,and rumor upon rumor.They will go searching for a vision from the prophet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20604AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20604AY\"></sup>priestly instruction in the law will cease,the counsel of the elders will come to an end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20604AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20604AZ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The king will mourn,the prince will be clothed with despair,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20605BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20605BA\"></sup>and the hands of the people of the land will tremble.I will deal with them according to their conduct,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20605BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20605BB\"></sup>and by their own standards I will judge them.“‘Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20605BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20605BC\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>In the sixth year, in the sixth month on the fifth day, while I was sitting in my house and the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20606A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20606A\"></sup> of Judah were sitting before<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20606B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20606B\"></sup> me, the hand of the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came on me there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20606C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20606C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I looked, and I saw a figure like that of a man. From what appeared to be his waist down he was like fire, and from there up his appearance was as bright as glowing metal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20607D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20607D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He stretched out what looked like a hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20608E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20608E\"></sup> and took me by the hair of my head. The Spirit lifted me up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20608F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20608F\"></sup> between earth and heaven and in visions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20608G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20608G\"></sup> of God he took me to Jerusalem, to the entrance of the north gate of the inner court,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20608H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20608H\"></sup> where the idol that provokes to jealousy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20608I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20608I\"></sup> stood.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And there before me was the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20609J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20609J\"></sup> of the God of Israel, as in the vision I had seen in the plain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20609K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20609K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then he said to me, “Son of man, look toward the north.” So I looked, and in the entrance north of the gate of the altar I saw this idol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20610L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20610L\"></sup> of jealousy.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he said to me, “Son of man, do you see what they are doing—the utterly detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20611M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20611M\"></sup> things the Israelites are doing here, things that will drive me far from my sanctuary?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20611N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20611N\"></sup> But you will see things that are even more detestable.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then he brought me to the entrance to the court. I looked, and I saw a hole in the wall.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, now dig into the wall.” So I dug into the wall and saw a doorway there.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he said to me, “Go in and see the wicked and detestable things they are doing here.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So I went in and looked, and I saw portrayed all over the walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20615O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20615O\"></sup> all kinds of crawling things and unclean<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20615P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20615P\"></sup> animals and all the idols of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20615Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20615Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In front of them stood seventy elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20616R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20616R\"></sup> of Israel, and Jaazaniah son of Shaphan was standing among them. Each had a censer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20616S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20616S\"></sup> in his hand, and a fragrant cloud of incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20616T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20616T\"></sup> was rising.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20616U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20616U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, have you seen what the elders of Israel are doing in the darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20617V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20617V\"></sup> each at the shrine of his own idol? They say, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not see<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20617W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20617W\"></sup> us; the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has forsaken the land.’”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Again, he said, “You will see them doing things that are even more detestable.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then he brought me to the entrance of the north gate of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I saw women sitting there, mourning the god Tammuz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20619X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20619X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He said to me, “Do you see this, son of man? You will see things that are even more detestable than this.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He then brought me into the inner court<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20621Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20621Y\"></sup> of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and there at the entrance to the temple, between the portico and the altar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20621Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20621Z\"></sup> were about twenty-five men. With their backs toward the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and their faces toward the east, they were bowing down to the sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20621AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20621AA\"></sup> in the east.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20621AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20621AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He said to me, “Have you seen this, son of man? Is it a trivial matter for the people of Judah to do the detestable things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20622AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20622AC\"></sup> they are doing here? Must they also fill the land with violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20622AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20622AD\"></sup> and continually arouse my anger?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20622AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20622AE\"></sup> Look at them putting the branch to their nose!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore I will deal with them in anger;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20623AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20623AF\"></sup> I will not look on them with pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20623AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20623AG\"></sup> or spare them. Although they shout in my ears, I will not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20623AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20623AH\"></sup> to them.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Then I heard him call out in a loud voice, “Bring near those who are appointed to execute judgment on the city, each with a weapon in his hand.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw six men coming from the direction of the upper gate, which faces north, each with a deadly weapon in his hand. With them was a man clothed in linen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20625A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20625A\"></sup> who had a writing kit at his side. They came in and stood beside the bronze altar.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20626B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20626B\"></sup> of the God of Israel went up from above the cherubim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20626C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20626C\"></sup> where it had been, and moved to the threshold of the temple. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> called to the man clothed in linen who had the writing kit at his side",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and said to him, “Go throughout the city of Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20627D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20627D\"></sup> and put a mark<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20627E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20627E\"></sup> on the foreheads of those who grieve and lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20627F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20627F\"></sup> over all the detestable things that are done in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20627G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20627G\"></sup>”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As I listened, he said to the others, “Follow him through the city and kill, without showing pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20628H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20628H\"></sup> or compassion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20628I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20628I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Slaughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20629J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20629J\"></sup> the old men, the young men and women, the mothers and children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20629K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20629K\"></sup> but do not touch anyone who has the mark.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20629L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20629L\"></sup> Begin at my sanctuary.” So they began with the old men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20629M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20629M\"></sup> who were in front of the temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20629N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20629N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then he said to them, “Defile the temple and fill the courts with the slain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20630O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20630O\"></sup> Go!” So they went out and began killing throughout the city.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>While they were killing and I was left alone, I fell facedown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20631P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20631P\"></sup> crying out, “Alas, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20631Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20631Q\"></sup> Are you going to destroy the entire remnant of Israel in this outpouring of your wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20631R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20631R\"></sup> on Jerusalem?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20631S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20631S\"></sup>”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He answered me, “The sin of the people of Israel and Judah is exceedingly great; the land is full of bloodshed and the city is full of injustice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20632T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20632T\"></sup> They say, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has forsaken the land; the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not see.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20632U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20632U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So I will not look on them with pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20633V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20633V\"></sup> or spare them, but I will bring down on their own heads what they have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20633W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20633W\"></sup>”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the man in linen with the writing kit at his side brought back word, saying, “I have done as you commanded.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>I looked, and I saw the likeness of a throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20635A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20635A\"></sup> of lapis lazuli<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20635B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20635B\"></sup> above the vault<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20635C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20635C\"></sup> that was over the heads of the cherubim.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20635D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20635D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to the man clothed in linen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20636E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20636E\"></sup> “Go in among the wheels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20636F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20636F\"></sup> beneath the cherubim. Fill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20636G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20636G\"></sup> your hands with burning coals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20636H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20636H\"></sup> from among the cherubim and scatter them over the city.” And as I watched, he went in.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now the cherubim were standing on the south side of the temple when the man went in, and a cloud filled the inner court.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20638I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20638I\"></sup> rose from above the cherubim and moved to the threshold of the temple. The cloud filled the temple, and the court was full of the radiance of the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The sound of the wings of the cherubim could be heard as far away as the outer court, like the voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20639J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20639J\"></sup> of God Almighty when he speaks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20639K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20639K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> commanded the man in linen, “Take fire from among the wheels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20640L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20640L\"></sup> from among the cherubim,” the man went in and stood beside a wheel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then one of the cherubim reached out his hand to the fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20641M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20641M\"></sup> that was among them. He took up some of it and put it into the hands of the man in linen, who took it and went out.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>(Under the wings of the cherubim could be seen what looked like human hands.)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20642N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20642N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I looked, and I saw beside the cherubim four wheels, one beside each of the cherubim; the wheels sparkled like topaz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20643O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20643O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As for their appearance, the four of them looked alike; each was like a wheel intersecting a wheel.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As they moved, they would go in any one of the four directions the cherubim faced; the wheels did not turn about as the cherubim went. The cherubim went in whatever direction the head faced, without turning as they went.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Their entire bodies, including their backs, their hands and their wings, were completely full of eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20646P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20646P\"></sup> as were their four wheels.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20646Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20646Q\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I heard the wheels being called “the whirling wheels.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Each of the cherubim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20648R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20648R\"></sup> had four faces:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20648S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20648S\"></sup> One face was that of a cherub, the second the face of a human being, the third the face of a lion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20648T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20648T\"></sup> and the fourth the face of an eagle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20648U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20648U\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the cherubim rose upward. These were the living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20649V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20649V\"></sup> I had seen by the Kebar River.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20649W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20649W\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When the cherubim moved, the wheels beside them moved; and when the cherubim spread their wings to rise from the ground, the wheels did not leave their side.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>When the cherubim stood still, they also stood still; and when the cherubim rose, they rose with them, because the spirit of the living creatures was in them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20651X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20651X\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20652Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20652Y\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> departed from over the threshold of the temple and stopped above the cherubim.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20652Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20652Z\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>While I watched, the cherubim spread their wings and rose from the ground, and as they went, the wheels went with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20653AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20653AA\"></sup> They stopped at the entrance of the east gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house, and the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20653AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20653AB\"></sup> of the God of Israel was above them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>These were the living creatures I had seen beneath the God of Israel by the Kebar River,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20654AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20654AC\"></sup> and I realized that they were cherubim.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Each had four faces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20655AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20655AD\"></sup> and four wings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20655AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20655AE\"></sup> and under their wings was what looked like human hands.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Their faces had the same appearance as those I had seen by the Kebar River.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20656AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20656AF\"></sup> Each one went straight ahead."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Then the Spirit lifted me up and brought me to the gate of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that faces east. There at the entrance of the gate were twenty-five men, and I saw among them Jaazaniah son of Azzur and Pelatiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20657A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20657A\"></sup> son of Benaiah, leaders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20657B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20657B\"></sup> of the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20657C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20657C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Son of man, these are the men who are plotting evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20658D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20658D\"></sup> and giving wicked advice in this city.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20658E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20658E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They say, ‘Haven’t our houses been recently rebuilt? This city is a pot,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20659F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20659F\"></sup> and we are the meat in it.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20659G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20659G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore prophesy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20660H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20660H\"></sup> against them; prophesy, son of man.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came on me, and he told me to say: “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: That is what you are saying, you leaders in Israel, but I know what is going through your mind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20661I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20661I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You have killed many people in this city and filled its streets with the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20662J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20662J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: The bodies you have thrown there are the meat and this city is the pot,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20663K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20663K\"></sup> but I will drive you out of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20663L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20663L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You fear the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20664M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20664M\"></sup> and the sword is what I will bring against you, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20664N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20664N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will drive you out of the city and deliver you into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20665O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20665O\"></sup> of foreigners and inflict punishment on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20665P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20665P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You will fall by the sword, and I will execute judgment on you at the borders of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20666Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20666Q\"></sup> Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This city will not be a pot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20667R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20667R\"></sup> for you, nor will you be the meat in it; I will execute judgment on you at the borders of Israel.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20668S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20668S\"></sup> for you have not followed my decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20668T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20668T\"></sup> or kept my laws but have conformed to the standards of the nations around you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20668U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20668U\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now as I was prophesying, Pelatiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20669V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20669V\"></sup> son of Benaiah died. Then I fell facedown and cried out in a loud voice, “Alas, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>! Will you completely destroy the remnant of Israel?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20669W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20669W\"></sup>”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Son of man, the people of Jerusalem have said of your fellow exiles and all the other Israelites, ‘They are far away from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; this land was given to us as our possession.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20671X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20671X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Therefore say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Although I sent them far away among the nations and scattered them among the countries, yet for a little while I have been a sanctuary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20672Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20672Y\"></sup> for them in the countries where they have gone.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Therefore say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will gather you from the nations and bring you back from the countries where you have been scattered, and I will give you back the land of Israel again.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20673Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20673Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“They will return to it and remove all its vile images<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20674AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20674AA\"></sup> and detestable idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20674AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20674AB\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will give them an undivided heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20675AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20675AC\"></sup> and put a new spirit in them; I will remove from them their heart of stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20675AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20675AD\"></sup> and give them a heart of flesh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20675AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20675AE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then they will follow my decrees and be careful to keep my laws.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20676AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20676AF\"></sup> They will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20676AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20676AG\"></sup> and I will be their God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20676AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20676AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But as for those whose hearts are devoted to their vile images and detestable idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20677AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20677AI\"></sup> I will bring down on their own heads what they have done, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20677AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20677AJ\"></sup>”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then the cherubim, with the wheels beside them, spread their wings, and the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20678AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20678AK\"></sup> of the God of Israel was above them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20678AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20678AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20679AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20679AM\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> went up from within the city and stopped above the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20679AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20679AN\"></sup> east of it.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20680AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20680AO\"></sup> lifted me up and brought me to the exiles in Babylonia in the vision<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20680AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20680AP\"></sup> given by the Spirit of God.Then the vision I had seen went up from me,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and I told the exiles everything the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had shown me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20681AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20681AQ\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, you are living among a rebellious people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20683A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20683A\"></sup> They have eyes to see but do not see and ears to hear but do not hear, for they are a rebellious people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20683B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20683B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Therefore, son of man, pack your belongings for exile and in the daytime, as they watch, set out and go from where you are to another place. Perhaps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20684C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20684C\"></sup> they will understand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20684D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20684D\"></sup> though they are a rebellious people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20684E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20684E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>During the daytime, while they watch, bring out your belongings packed for exile. Then in the evening, while they are watching, go out like those who go into exile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20685F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20685F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>While they watch, dig through the wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20686G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20686G\"></sup> and take your belongings out through it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Put them on your shoulder as they are watching and carry them out at dusk. Cover your face so that you cannot see the land, for I have made you a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20687H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20687H\"></sup> to the Israelites.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I did as I was commanded.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20688I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20688I\"></sup> During the day I brought out my things packed for exile. Then in the evening I dug through the wall with my hands. I took my belongings out at dusk, carrying them on my shoulders while they watched.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the morning the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Son of man, did not the Israelites, that rebellious people, ask you, ‘What are you doing?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20690J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20690J\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: This prophecy concerns the prince in Jerusalem and all the Israelites who are there.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Say to them, ‘I am a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20692K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20692K\"></sup> to you.’“As I have done, so it will be done to them. They will go into exile as captives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20692L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20692L\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“The prince among them will put his things on his shoulder at dusk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20693M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20693M\"></sup> and leave, and a hole will be dug in the wall for him to go through. He will cover his face so that he cannot see the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20693N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20693N\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will spread my net<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20694O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20694O\"></sup> for him, and he will be caught in my snare;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20694P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20694P\"></sup> I will bring him to Babylonia, the land of the Chaldeans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20694Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20694Q\"></sup> but he will not see<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20694R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20694R\"></sup> it, and there he will die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20694S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20694S\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will scatter to the winds all those around him—his staff and all his troops—and I will pursue them with drawn sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20695T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20695T\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“They will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I disperse them among the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20696U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20696U\"></sup> and scatter them through the countries.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But I will spare a few of them from the sword, famine and plague, so that in the nations where they go they may acknowledge all their detestable practices. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20697V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20697V\"></sup>”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, tremble as you eat your food,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20699W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20699W\"></sup> and shudder in fear as you drink your water.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Say to the people of the land: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about those living in Jerusalem and in the land of Israel: They will eat their food in anxiety and drink their water in despair, for their land will be stripped of everything<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20700X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20700X\"></sup> in it because of the violence of all who live there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20700Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20700Y\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The inhabited towns will be laid waste and the land will be desolate. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20701Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20701Z\"></sup>’”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Son of man, what is this proverb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20703AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20703AA\"></sup> you have in the land of Israel: ‘The days go by and every vision comes to nothing’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20703AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20703AB\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am going to put an end to this proverb, and they will no longer quote it in Israel.’ Say to them, ‘The days are near<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20704AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20704AC\"></sup> when every vision will be fulfilled.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20704AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20704AD\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For there will be no more false visions or flattering divinations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20705AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20705AE\"></sup> among the people of Israel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will speak what I will, and it shall be fulfilled without delay.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20706AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20706AF\"></sup> For in your days, you rebellious people, I will fulfill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20706AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20706AG\"></sup> whatever I say, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20706AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20706AH\"></sup>’”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Son of man, the Israelites are saying, ‘The vision he sees is for many years from now, and he prophesies about the distant future.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20708AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20708AI\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Therefore say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: None of my words will be delayed any longer; whatever I say will be fulfilled, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy against the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20711A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20711A\"></sup> of Israel who are now prophesying. Say to those who prophesy out of their own imagination:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20711B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20711B\"></sup> ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20711C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20711C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Woe to the foolish prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20712D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20712D\"></sup> who follow their own spirit and have seen nothing!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20712E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20712E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your prophets, Israel, are like jackals among ruins.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You have not gone up to the breaches in the wall to repair<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20714F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20714F\"></sup> it for the people of Israel so that it will stand firm in the battle on the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20714G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20714G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Their visions are false<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20715H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20715H\"></sup> and their divinations a lie. Even though the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20715I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20715I\"></sup> them, they say, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares,” and expect him to fulfill their words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20715J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20715J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Have you not seen false visions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20716K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20716K\"></sup> and uttered lying divinations when you say, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares,” though I have not spoken?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Because of your false words and lying visions, I am against you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20717L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20717L\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>My hand will be against the prophets who see false visions and utter lying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20718M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20718M\"></sup> divinations. They will not belong to the council of my people or be listed in the records<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20718N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20718N\"></sup> of Israel, nor will they enter the land of Israel. Then you will know that I am the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20718O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20718O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘Because they lead my people astray,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20719P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20719P\"></sup> saying, “Peace,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20719Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20719Q\"></sup> when there is no peace, and because, when a flimsy wall is built, they cover it with whitewash,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20719R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20719R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>therefore tell those who cover it with whitewash that it is going to fall. Rain will come in torrents, and I will send hailstones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20720S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20720S\"></sup> hurtling down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20720T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20720T\"></sup> and violent winds will burst forth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20720U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20720U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When the wall collapses, will people not ask you, “Where is the whitewash you covered it with?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: In my wrath I will unleash a violent wind, and in my anger hailstones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20722V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20722V\"></sup> and torrents of rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20722W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20722W\"></sup> will fall with destructive fury.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20722X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20722X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will tear down the wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20723Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20723Y\"></sup> you have covered with whitewash and will level it to the ground so that its foundation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20723Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20723Z\"></sup> will be laid bare. When it falls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20723AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20723AA\"></sup> you will be destroyed in it; and you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So I will pour out my wrath against the wall and against those who covered it with whitewash. I will say to you, “The wall is gone and so are those who whitewashed it,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>those prophets of Israel who prophesied to Jerusalem and saw visions of peace for her when there was no peace, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20725AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20725AB\"></sup>”’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Now, son of man, set your face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20726AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20726AC\"></sup> against the daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20726AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20726AD\"></sup> of your people who prophesy out of their own imagination. Prophesy against them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20726AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20726AE\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and say, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Woe to the women who sew magic charms on all their wrists and make veils of various lengths for their heads in order to ensnare people. Will you ensnare the lives of my people but preserve your own?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You have profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20728AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20728AF\"></sup> me among my people for a few handfuls of barley and scraps of bread.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20728AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20728AG\"></sup> By lying to my people, who listen to lies, you have killed those who should not have died and have spared those who should not live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20728AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20728AH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against your magic charms with which you ensnare people like birds and I will tear them from your arms; I will set free the people that you ensnare like birds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20729AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20729AI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will tear off your veils and save my people from your hands, and they will no longer fall prey to your power. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20730AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20730AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Because you disheartened the righteous with your lies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20731AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20731AK\"></sup> when I had brought them no grief, and because you encouraged the wicked not to turn from their evil ways and so save their lives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20731AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20731AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>therefore you will no longer see false visions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20732AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20732AM\"></sup> or practice divination.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20732AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20732AN\"></sup> I will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20732AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20732AO\"></sup> my people from your hands. And then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20732AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20732AP\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Some of the elders of Israel came to me and sat down in front of me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20733A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20733A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Son of man, these men have set up idols in their hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20735B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20735B\"></sup> and put wicked stumbling blocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20735C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20735C\"></sup> before their faces. Should I let them inquire of me at all?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20735D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20735D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore speak to them and tell them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: When any of the Israelites set up idols in their hearts and put a wicked stumbling block before their faces and then go to a prophet, I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer them myself in keeping with their great idolatry.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will do this to recapture the hearts of the people of Israel, who have all deserted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20737E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20737E\"></sup> me for their idols.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20737F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20737F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Therefore say to the people of Israel, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Repent!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20738G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20738G\"></sup> Turn from your idols and renounce all your detestable practices!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20738H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20738H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘When any of the Israelites or any foreigner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20739I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20739I\"></sup> residing in Israel separate themselves from me and set up idols in their hearts and put a wicked stumbling block<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20739J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20739J\"></sup> before their faces and then go to a prophet to inquire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20739K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20739K\"></sup> of me, I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer them myself.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will set my face against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20740L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20740L\"></sup> them and make them an example<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20740M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20740M\"></sup> and a byword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20740N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20740N\"></sup> I will remove them from my people. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20740O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20740O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘And if the prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20741P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20741P\"></sup> is enticed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20741Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20741Q\"></sup> to utter a prophecy, I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have enticed that prophet, and I will stretch out my hand against him and destroy him from among my people Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20741R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20741R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will bear their guilt—the prophet will be as guilty as the one who consults him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the people of Israel will no longer stray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20743S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20743S\"></sup> from me, nor will they defile themselves anymore with all their sins. They will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20743T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20743T\"></sup> and I will be their God, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20743U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20743U\"></sup>’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Son of man, if a country sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20745V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20745V\"></sup> against me by being unfaithful and I stretch out my hand against it to cut off its food supply<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20745W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20745W\"></sup> and send famine upon it and kill its people and their animals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20745X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20745X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>even if these three men—Noah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20746Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20746Y\"></sup> Daniel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20746Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20746Z\"></sup> and Job<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20746AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20746AA\"></sup>—were in it, they could save only themselves by their righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20746AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20746AB\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Or if I send wild beasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20747AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20747AC\"></sup> through that country and they leave it childless and it becomes desolate so that no one can pass through it because of the beasts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20747AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20747AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>as surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, even if these three men were in it, they could not save their own sons or daughters. They alone would be saved, but the land would be desolate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20748AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20748AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Or if I bring a sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20749AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20749AF\"></sup> against that country and say, ‘Let the sword pass throughout the land,’ and I kill its people and their animals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20749AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20749AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>as surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, even if these three men were in it, they could not save their own sons or daughters. They alone would be saved.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Or if I send a plague into that land and pour out my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20751AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20751AH\"></sup> on it through bloodshed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20751AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20751AI\"></sup> killing its people and their animals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20751AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20751AJ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>as surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, even if Noah, Daniel and Job were in it, they could save neither son nor daughter. They would save only themselves by their righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20752AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20752AK\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: How much worse will it be when I send against Jerusalem my four dreadful judgments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20753AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20753AL\"></sup>—sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20753AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20753AM\"></sup> and famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20753AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20753AN\"></sup> and wild beasts and plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20753AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20753AO\"></sup>—to kill its men and their animals!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20753AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20753AP\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Yet there will be some survivors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20754AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20754AQ\"></sup>—sons and daughters who will be brought out of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20754AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20754AR\"></sup> They will come to you, and when you see their conduct<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20754AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20754AS\"></sup> and their actions, you will be consoled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20754AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20754AT\"></sup> regarding the disaster I have brought on Jerusalem—every disaster I have brought on it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>You will be consoled when you see their conduct and their actions, for you will know that I have done nothing in it without cause, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20755AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20755AU\"></sup>”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, how is the wood of a vine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20757A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20757A\"></sup> different from that of a branch from any of the trees in the forest?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Is wood ever taken from it to make anything useful?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20758B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20758B\"></sup> Do they make pegs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20758C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20758C\"></sup> from it to hang things on?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And after it is thrown on the fire as fuel and the fire burns both ends and chars the middle, is it then useful for anything?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20759D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20759D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If it was not useful for anything when it was whole, how much less can it be made into something useful when the fire has burned it and it is charred?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: As I have given the wood of the vine among the trees of the forest as fuel for the fire, so will I treat the people living in Jerusalem.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will set my face against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20762E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20762E\"></sup> them. Although they have come out of the fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20762F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20762F\"></sup>, the fire will yet consume them. And when I set my face against them, you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20762G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20762G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will make the land desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20763H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20763H\"></sup> because they have been unfaithful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20763I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20763I\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, confront<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20765A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20765A\"></sup> Jerusalem with her detestable practices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20765B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20765B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to Jerusalem: Your ancestry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20766C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20766C\"></sup> and birth were in the land of the Canaanites; your father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20766D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20766D\"></sup> was an Amorite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20766E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20766E\"></sup> and your mother a Hittite.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20766F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20766F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>On the day you were born<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20767G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20767G\"></sup> your cord was not cut, nor were you washed with water to make you clean, nor were you rubbed with salt or wrapped in cloths.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>No one looked on you with pity or had compassion enough to do any of these things for you. Rather, you were thrown out into the open field, for on the day you were born you were despised.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘Then I passed by and saw you kicking about in your blood, and as you lay there in your blood I said to you, “Live!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20769H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20769H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I made you grow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20770I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20770I\"></sup> like a plant of the field. You grew and developed and entered puberty. Your breasts had formed and your hair had grown, yet you were stark naked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20770J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20770J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘Later I passed by, and when I looked at you and saw that you were old enough for love, I spread the corner of my garment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20771K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20771K\"></sup> over you and covered your naked body. I gave you my solemn oath and entered into a covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20771L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20771L\"></sup> with you, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and you became mine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20771M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20771M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘I bathed you with water and washed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20772N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20772N\"></sup> the blood from you and put ointments on you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I clothed you with an embroidered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20773O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20773O\"></sup> dress and put sandals of fine leather on you. I dressed you in fine linen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20773P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20773P\"></sup> and covered you with costly garments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20773Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20773Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I adorned you with jewelry:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20774R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20774R\"></sup> I put bracelets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20774S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20774S\"></sup> on your arms and a necklace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20774T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20774T\"></sup> around your neck,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and I put a ring on your nose,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20775U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20775U\"></sup> earrings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20775V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20775V\"></sup> on your ears and a beautiful crown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20775W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20775W\"></sup> on your head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20775X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20775X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So you were adorned with gold and silver; your clothes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20776Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20776Y\"></sup> were of fine linen and costly fabric and embroidered cloth. Your food was honey, olive oil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20776Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20776Z\"></sup> and the finest flour. You became very beautiful and rose to be a queen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20776AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20776AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And your fame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20777AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20777AB\"></sup> spread among the nations on account of your beauty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20777AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20777AC\"></sup> because the splendor I had given you made your beauty perfect, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20777AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20777AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“‘But you trusted in your beauty and used your fame to become a prostitute. You lavished your favors on anyone who passed by<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20778AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20778AE\"></sup> and your beauty became his.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20778AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20778AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You took some of your garments to make gaudy high places,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20779AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20779AG\"></sup> where you carried on your prostitution.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20779AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20779AH\"></sup> You went to him, and he possessed your beauty.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You also took the fine jewelry I gave you, the jewelry made of my gold and silver, and you made for yourself male idols and engaged in prostitution with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20780AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20780AI\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And you took your embroidered clothes to put on them, and you offered my oil and incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20781AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20781AJ\"></sup> before them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Also the food I provided for you—the flour, olive oil and honey I gave you to eat—you offered as fragrant incense before them. That is what happened, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20782AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20782AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“‘And you took your sons and daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20783AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20783AL\"></sup> whom you bore to me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20783AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20783AM\"></sup> and sacrificed them as food to the idols. Was your prostitution not enough?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20783AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20783AN\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You slaughtered my children and sacrificed them to the idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20784AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20784AO\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In all your detestable practices and your prostitution you did not remember the days of your youth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20785AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20785AP\"></sup> when you were naked and bare,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20785AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20785AQ\"></sup> kicking about in your blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20785AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20785AR\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“‘Woe!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20786AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20786AS\"></sup> Woe to you, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. In addition to all your other wickedness,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>you built a mound for yourself and made a lofty shrine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20787AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20787AT\"></sup> in every public square.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20787AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20787AU\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>At every street corner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20788AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20788AV\"></sup> you built your lofty shrines and degraded your beauty, spreading your legs with increasing promiscuity to anyone who passed by.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20788AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20788AW\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You engaged in prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20789AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20789AX\"></sup> with the Egyptians,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20789AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20789AY\"></sup> your neighbors with large genitals, and aroused my anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20789AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20789AZ\"></sup> with your increasing promiscuity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20789BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20789BA\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So I stretched out my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20790BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20790BB\"></sup> against you and reduced your territory; I gave you over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20790BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20790BC\"></sup> to the greed of your enemies, the daughters of the Philistines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20790BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20790BD\"></sup> who were shocked by your lewd conduct.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You engaged in prostitution with the Assyrians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20791BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20791BE\"></sup> too, because you were insatiable; and even after that, you still were not satisfied.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20791BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20791BF\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then you increased your promiscuity to include Babylonia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20792BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20792BG\"></sup> a land of merchants, but even with this you were not satisfied.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20792BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20792BH\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“‘I am filled with fury against you, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when you do all these things, acting like a brazen prostitute!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20793BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20793BI\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When you built your mounds at every street corner and made your lofty shrines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20794BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20794BJ\"></sup> in every public square, you were unlike a prostitute, because you scorned payment.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“‘You adulterous wife! You prefer strangers to your own husband!",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>All prostitutes receive gifts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20796BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20796BK\"></sup> but you give gifts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20796BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20796BL\"></sup> to all your lovers, bribing them to come to you from everywhere for your illicit favors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20796BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20796BM\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>So in your prostitution you are the opposite of others; no one runs after you for your favors. You are the very opposite, for you give payment and none is given to you.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“‘Therefore, you prostitute, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Because you poured out your lust and exposed your naked body in your promiscuity with your lovers, and because of all your detestable idols, and because you gave them your children’s blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20799BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20799BN\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>therefore I am going to gather all your lovers, with whom you found pleasure, those you loved as well as those you hated. I will gather them against you from all around and will strip<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20800BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20800BO\"></sup> you in front of them, and they will see you stark naked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20800BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20800BP\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>I will sentence you to the punishment of women who commit adultery and who shed blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20801BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20801BQ\"></sup> I will bring on you the blood vengeance of my wrath and jealous anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20801BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20801BR\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Then I will deliver you into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20802BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20802BS\"></sup> of your lovers, and they will tear down your mounds and destroy your lofty shrines. They will strip you of your clothes and take your fine jewelry and leave you stark naked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20802BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20802BT\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>They will bring a mob against you, who will stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20803BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20803BU\"></sup> you and hack you to pieces with their swords.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>They will burn down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20804BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20804BV\"></sup> your houses and inflict punishment on you in the sight of many women.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20804BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20804BW\"></sup> I will put a stop<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20804BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20804BX\"></sup> to your prostitution, and you will no longer pay your lovers.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Then my wrath against you will subside and my jealous anger will turn away from you; I will be calm and no longer angry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20805BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20805BY\"></sup>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“‘Because you did not remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20806BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20806BZ\"></sup> the days of your youth but enraged me with all these things, I will surely bring down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20806CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20806CA\"></sup> on your head what you have done, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Did you not add lewdness to all your other detestable practices?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20806CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20806CB\"></sup>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“‘Everyone who quotes proverbs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20807CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20807CC\"></sup> will quote this proverb about you: “Like mother, like daughter.”",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>You are a true daughter of your mother, who despised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20808CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20808CD\"></sup> her husband<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20808CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20808CE\"></sup> and her children; and you are a true sister of your sisters, who despised their husbands and their children. Your mother was a Hittite and your father an Amorite.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20808CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20808CF\"></sup>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Your older sister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20809CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20809CG\"></sup> was Samaria, who lived to the north of you with her daughters; and your younger sister, who lived to the south of you with her daughters, was Sodom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20809CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20809CH\"></sup>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>You not only followed their ways and copied their detestable practices, but in all your ways you soon became more depraved than they.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20810CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20810CI\"></sup>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>As surely as I live, declares the Sovereign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20811CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20811CJ\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your sister Sodom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20811CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20811CK\"></sup> and her daughters never did what you and your daughters have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20811CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20811CL\"></sup>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>“‘Now this was the sin of your sister Sodom:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20812CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20812CM\"></sup> She and her daughters were arrogant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20812CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20812CN\"></sup> overfed and unconcerned;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20812CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20812CO\"></sup> they did not help the poor and needy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20812CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20812CP\"></sup>",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>They were haughty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20813CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20813CQ\"></sup> and did detestable things before me. Therefore I did away with them as you have seen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20813CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20813CR\"></sup>",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>Samaria did not commit half the sins you did. You have done more detestable things than they, and have made your sisters seem righteous by all these things you have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20814CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20814CS\"></sup>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>Bear your disgrace, for you have furnished some justification for your sisters. Because your sins were more vile than theirs, they appear more righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20815CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20815CT\"></sup> than you. So then, be ashamed and bear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20815CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20815CU\"></sup> your disgrace, for you have made your sisters appear righteous.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>“‘However, I will restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20816CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20816CV\"></sup> the fortunes of Sodom and her daughters and of Samaria and her daughters, and your fortunes along with them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20816CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20816CW\"></sup>",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>so that you may bear your disgrace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20817CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20817CX\"></sup> and be ashamed of all you have done in giving them comfort.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>And your sisters, Sodom with her daughters and Samaria with her daughters, will return to what they were before; and you and your daughters will return to what you were before.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20818CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20818CY\"></sup>",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>You would not even mention your sister Sodom in the day of your pride,",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>before your wickedness was uncovered. Even so, you are now scorned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20820CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20820CZ\"></sup> by the daughters of Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20820DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20820DA\"></sup> and all her neighbors and the daughters of the Philistines—all those around you who despise you.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>You will bear the consequences of your lewdness and your detestable practices, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20821DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20821DB\"></sup>",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will deal with you as you deserve, because you have despised my oath by breaking the covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20822DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20822DC\"></sup>",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>Yet I will remember the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20823DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20823DD\"></sup> I made with you in the days of your youth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20823DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20823DE\"></sup> and I will establish an everlasting covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20823DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20823DF\"></sup> with you.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>Then you will remember your ways and be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20824DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20824DG\"></sup> when you receive your sisters, both those who are older than you and those who are younger. I will give them to you as daughters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20824DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20824DH\"></sup> but not on the basis of my covenant with you.",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>So I will establish my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20825DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20825DI\"></sup> with you, and you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20825DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20825DJ\"></sup>",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>Then, when I make atonement<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20826DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20826DK\"></sup> for you for all you have done, you will remember and be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20826DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20826DL\"></sup> and never again open your mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20826DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20826DM\"></sup> because of your humiliation, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20826DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20826DN\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set forth an allegory and tell it to the Israelites as a parable.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20828A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20828A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: A great eagle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20829B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20829B\"></sup> with powerful wings, long feathers and full plumage of varied colors came to Lebanon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20829C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20829C\"></sup> Taking hold of the top of a cedar,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>he broke off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20830D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20830D\"></sup> its topmost shoot and carried it away to a land of merchants, where he planted it in a city of traders.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“‘He took one of the seedlings of the land and put it in fertile soil. He planted it like a willow by abundant water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20831E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20831E\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and it sprouted and became a low, spreading vine. Its branches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20832F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20832F\"></sup> turned toward him, but its roots remained under it. So it became a vine and produced branches and put out leafy boughs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20832G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20832G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘But there was another great eagle with powerful wings and full plumage. The vine now sent out its roots toward him from the plot where it was planted and stretched out its branches to him for water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20833H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20833H\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It had been planted in good soil by abundant water so that it would produce branches,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20834I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20834I\"></sup> bear fruit and become a splendid vine.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Will it thrive? Will it not be uprooted and stripped of its fruit so that it withers? All its new growth will wither. It will not take a strong arm or many people to pull it up by the roots.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20835J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20835J\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>It has been planted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20836K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20836K\"></sup> but will it thrive? Will it not wither completely when the east wind strikes it—wither away in the plot where it grew?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20836L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20836L\"></sup>’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Say to this rebellious people, ‘Do you not know what these things mean?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20838M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20838M\"></sup>’ Say to them: ‘The king of Babylon went to Jerusalem and carried off her king and her nobles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20838N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20838N\"></sup> bringing them back with him to Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20838O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20838O\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he took a member of the royal family and made a treaty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20839P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20839P\"></sup> with him, putting him under oath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20839Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20839Q\"></sup> He also carried away the leading men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20839R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20839R\"></sup> of the land,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>so that the kingdom would be brought low,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20840S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20840S\"></sup> unable to rise again, surviving only by keeping his treaty.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But the king rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20841T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20841T\"></sup> against him by sending his envoys to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20841U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20841U\"></sup> to get horses and a large army.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20841V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20841V\"></sup> Will he succeed? Will he who does such things escape? Will he break the treaty and yet escape?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20841W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20841W\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“‘As surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, he shall die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20842X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20842X\"></sup> in Babylon, in the land of the king who put him on the throne, whose oath he despised and whose treaty he broke.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20842Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20842Y\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Pharaoh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20843Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20843Z\"></sup> with his mighty army and great horde will be of no help to him in war, when ramps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20843AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20843AA\"></sup> are built and siege works erected to destroy many lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20843AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20843AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He despised the oath by breaking the covenant. Because he had given his hand in pledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20844AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20844AC\"></sup> and yet did all these things, he shall not escape.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: As surely as I live, I will repay him for despising my oath and breaking my covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20845AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20845AD\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I will spread my net<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20846AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20846AE\"></sup> for him, and he will be caught in my snare. I will bring him to Babylon and execute judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20846AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20846AF\"></sup> on him there because he was unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20846AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20846AG\"></sup> to me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>All his choice troops will fall by the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20847AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20847AH\"></sup> and the survivors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20847AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20847AI\"></sup> will be scattered to the winds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20847AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20847AJ\"></sup> Then you will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20847AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20847AK\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I myself will take a shoot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20848AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20848AL\"></sup> from the very top of a cedar and plant it; I will break off a tender sprig from its topmost shoots and plant it on a high and lofty mountain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20848AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20848AM\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>On the mountain heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20849AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20849AN\"></sup> of Israel I will plant it; it will produce branches and bear fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20849AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20849AO\"></sup> and become a splendid cedar. Birds of every kind will nest in it; they will find shelter in the shade of its branches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20849AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20849AP\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>All the trees of the forest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20850AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20850AQ\"></sup> will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> bring down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20850AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20850AR\"></sup> the tall tree and make the low tree grow tall. I dry up the green tree and make the dry tree flourish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20850AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20850AS\"></sup>“‘I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken, and I will do it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20850AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20850AT\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“What do you people mean by quoting this proverb about the land of Israel:“‘The parents eat sour grapes,and the children’s teeth are set on edge’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20852A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20852A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“As surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you will no longer quote this proverb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20853B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20853B\"></sup> in Israel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For everyone belongs to me, the parent as well as the child—both alike belong to me. The one who sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20854C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20854C\"></sup> is the one who will die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20854D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20854D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Suppose there is a righteous manwho does what is just and right.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He does not eat at the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20856E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20856E\"></sup> shrinesor look to the idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20856F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20856F\"></sup> of Israel.He does not defile his neighbor’s wifeor have sexual relations with a woman during her period.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20856G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20856G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He does not oppress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20857H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20857H\"></sup> anyone,but returns what he took in pledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20857I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20857I\"></sup> for a loan.He does not commit robbery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20857J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20857J\"></sup>but gives his food to the hungry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20857K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20857K\"></sup>and provides clothing for the naked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20857L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20857L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He does not lend to them at interestor take a profit from them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20858M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20858M\"></sup>He withholds his hand from doing wrongand judges fairly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20858N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20858N\"></sup> between two parties.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He follows my decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20859O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20859O\"></sup>and faithfully keeps my laws.That man is righteous;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20859P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20859P\"></sup>he will surely live,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20859Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20859Q\"></sup>declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Suppose he has a violent son, who sheds blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20860R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20860R\"></sup> or does any of these other things",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>(though the father has done none of them):“He eats at the mountain shrines.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20861S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20861S\"></sup>He defiles his neighbor’s wife.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He oppresses the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20862T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20862T\"></sup> and needy.He commits robbery.He does not return what he took in pledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20862U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20862U\"></sup>He looks to the idols.He does detestable things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20862V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20862V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He lends at interest and takes a profit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20863W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20863W\"></sup>Will such a man live? He will not! Because he has done all these detestable things, he is to be put to death; his blood will be on his own head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20863X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20863X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“But suppose this son has a son who sees all the sins his father commits, and though he sees them, he does not do such things:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20864Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20864Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“He does not eat at the mountain shrines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20865Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20865Z\"></sup>or look to the idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20865AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20865AA\"></sup> of Israel.He does not defile his neighbor’s wife.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He does not oppress anyoneor require a pledge for a loan.He does not commit robberybut gives his food to the hungry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20866AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20866AB\"></sup>and provides clothing for the naked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20866AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20866AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He withholds his hand from mistreating the poorand takes no interest or profit from them.He keeps my laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20867AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20867AD\"></sup> and follows my decrees.He will not die for his father’s sin; he will surely live.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But his father will die for his own sin, because he practiced extortion, robbed his brother and did what was wrong among his people.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Yet you ask, ‘Why does the son not share the guilt of his father?’ Since the son has done what is just and right and has been careful to keep all my decrees, he will surely live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20869AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20869AE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The one who sins is the one who will die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20870AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20870AF\"></sup> The child will not share the guilt of the parent, nor will the parent share the guilt of the child. The righteousness of the righteous will be credited to them, and the wickedness of the wicked will be charged against them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20870AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20870AG\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“But if<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20871AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20871AH\"></sup> a wicked person turns away from all the sins they have committed and keeps all my decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20871AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20871AI\"></sup> and does what is just and right, that person will surely live; they will not die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20871AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20871AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>None of the offenses they have committed will be remembered against them. Because of the righteous things they have done, they will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20872AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20872AK\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Do I take any pleasure in the death of the wicked? declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Rather, am I not pleased<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20873AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20873AL\"></sup> when they turn from their ways and live?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20873AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20873AM\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“But if a righteous person turns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20874AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20874AN\"></sup> from their righteousness and commits sin and does the same detestable things the wicked person does, will they live? None of the righteous things that person has done will be remembered. Because of the unfaithfulness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20874AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20874AO\"></sup> they are guilty of and because of the sins they have committed, they will die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20874AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20874AP\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Yet you say, ‘The way of the Lord is not just.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20875AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20875AQ\"></sup> Hear, you Israelites: Is my way unjust?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20875AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20875AR\"></sup> Is it not your ways that are unjust?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If a righteous person turns from their righteousness and commits sin, they will die for it; because of the sin they have committed they will die.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But if a wicked person turns away from the wickedness they have committed and does what is just and right, they will save their life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20877AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20877AS\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Because they consider all the offenses they have committed and turn away from them, that person will surely live; they will not die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20878AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20878AT\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Yet the Israelites say, ‘The way of the Lord is not just.’ Are my ways unjust, people of Israel? Is it not your ways that are unjust?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Therefore, you Israelites, I will judge each of you according to your own ways, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Repent!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20880AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20880AU\"></sup> Turn away from all your offenses; then sin will not be your downfall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20880AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20880AV\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Rid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20881AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20881AW\"></sup> yourselves of all the offenses you have committed, and get a new heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20881AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20881AX\"></sup> and a new spirit. Why<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20881AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20881AY\"></sup> will you die, people of Israel?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20881AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20881AZ\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For I take no pleasure in the death of anyone, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20882BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20882BA\"></sup> and live!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20882BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20882BB\"></sup>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>“Take up a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20883A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20883A\"></sup> concerning the princes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20883B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20883B\"></sup> of Israel",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and say:“‘What a lioness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20884C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20884C\"></sup> was your motheramong the lions!She lay down among themand reared her cubs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20884D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20884D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>She brought up one of her cubs,and he became a strong lion.He learned to tear the preyand he became a man-eater.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The nations heard about him,and he was trapped in their pit.They led him with hooks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20886E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20886E\"></sup>to the land of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20886F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20886F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“‘When she saw her hope unfulfilled,her expectation gone,she took another of her cubs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20887G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20887G\"></sup>and made him a strong lion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20887H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20887H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He prowled among the lions,for he was now a strong lion.He learned to tear the preyand he became a man-eater.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20888I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20888I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He broke down their strongholdsand devastated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20889J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20889J\"></sup> their towns.The land and all who were in itwere terrified by his roaring.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20890K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20890K\"></sup> came against him,those from regions round about.They spread their net<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20890L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20890L\"></sup> for him,and he was trapped in their pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20890M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20890M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>With hooks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20891N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20891N\"></sup> they pulled him into a cageand brought him to the king of Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20891O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20891O\"></sup>They put him in prison,so his roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20891P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20891P\"></sup> was heard no longeron the mountains of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20891Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20891Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘Your mother was like a vine in your vineyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20892R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20892R\"></sup>planted by the water;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20892S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20892S\"></sup>it was fruitful and full of branchesbecause of abundant water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20892T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20892T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Its branches were strong,fit for a ruler’s scepter.It towered highabove the thick foliage,conspicuous for its heightand for its many branches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20893U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20893U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But it was uprooted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20894V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20894V\"></sup> in furyand thrown to the ground.The east wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20894W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20894W\"></sup> made it shrivel,it was stripped of its fruit;its strong branches witheredand fire consumed them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20894X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20894X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now it is planted in the desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20895Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20895Y\"></sup>in a dry and thirsty land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20895Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20895Z\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Fire spread from one of its main branchesand consumed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20896AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20896AA\"></sup> its fruit.No strong branch is left on itfit for a ruler’s scepter.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20896AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20896AB\"></sup>“This is a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20896AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20896AC\"></sup> and is to be used as a lament.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>In the seventh year, in the fifth month on the tenth day, some of the elders of Israel came to inquire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20897A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20897A\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and they sat down in front of me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20897B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20897B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Son of man, speak to the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20899C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20899C\"></sup> of Israel and say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Have you come to inquire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20899D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20899D\"></sup> of me? As surely as I live, I will not let you inquire of me, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20899E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20899E\"></sup>’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Will you judge them? Will you judge them, son of man? Then confront them with the detestable practices of their ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20900F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20900F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and say to them: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: On the day I chose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20901G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20901G\"></sup> Israel, I swore with uplifted hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20901H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20901H\"></sup> to the descendants of Jacob and revealed myself to them in Egypt. With uplifted hand I said to them, “I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20901I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20901I\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On that day I swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20902J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20902J\"></sup> to them that I would bring them out of Egypt into a land I had searched out for them, a land flowing with milk and honey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20902K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20902K\"></sup> the most beautiful of all lands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20902L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20902L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I said to them, “Each of you, get rid of the vile images<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20903M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20903M\"></sup> you have set your eyes on, and do not defile yourselves with the idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20903N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20903N\"></sup> of Egypt. I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20903O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20903O\"></sup>”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘But they rebelled against me and would not listen to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20904P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20904P\"></sup> they did not get rid of the vile images they had set their eyes on, nor did they forsake the idols of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20904Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20904Q\"></sup> So I said I would pour out my wrath on them and spend my anger against them in Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20904R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20904R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But for the sake of my name, I brought them out of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20905S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20905S\"></sup> I did it to keep my name from being profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20905T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20905T\"></sup> in the eyes of the nations among whom they lived and in whose sight I had revealed myself to the Israelites.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore I led them out of Egypt and brought them into the wilderness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20906U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20906U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I gave them my decrees and made known to them my laws, by which the person who obeys them will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20907V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20907V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Also I gave them my Sabbaths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20908W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20908W\"></sup> as a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20908X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20908X\"></sup> between us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20908Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20908Y\"></sup> so they would know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> made them holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20908Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20908Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘Yet the people of Israel rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20909AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20909AA\"></sup> against me in the wilderness. They did not follow my decrees but rejected my laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20909AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20909AB\"></sup>—by which the person who obeys them will live—and they utterly desecrated my Sabbaths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20909AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20909AC\"></sup> So I said I would pour out my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20909AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20909AD\"></sup> on them and destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20909AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20909AE\"></sup> them in the wilderness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20909AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20909AF\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But for the sake of my name I did what would keep it from being profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20910AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20910AG\"></sup> in the eyes of the nations in whose sight I had brought them out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20910AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20910AH\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Also with uplifted hand I swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20911AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20911AI\"></sup> to them in the wilderness that I would not bring them into the land I had given them—a land flowing with milk and honey, the most beautiful of all lands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20911AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20911AJ\"></sup>—",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>because they rejected my laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20912AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20912AK\"></sup> and did not follow my decrees and desecrated my Sabbaths. For their hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20912AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20912AL\"></sup> were devoted to their idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20912AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20912AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Yet I looked on them with pity and did not destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20913AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20913AN\"></sup> them or put an end to them in the wilderness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I said to their children in the wilderness, “Do not follow the statutes of your parents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20914AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20914AO\"></sup> or keep their laws or defile yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20914AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20914AP\"></sup> with their idols.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20915AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20915AQ\"></sup> follow my decrees and be careful to keep my laws.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20915AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20915AR\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Keep my Sabbaths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20916AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20916AS\"></sup> holy, that they may be a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20916AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20916AT\"></sup> between us. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20916AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20916AU\"></sup>”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“‘But the children rebelled against me: They did not follow my decrees, they were not careful to keep my laws,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20917AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20917AV\"></sup> of which I said, “The person who obeys them will live by them,” and they desecrated my Sabbaths. So I said I would pour out my wrath on them and spend my anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20917AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20917AW\"></sup> against them in the wilderness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20917AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20917AX\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But I withheld<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20918AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20918AY\"></sup> my hand, and for the sake of my name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20918AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20918AZ\"></sup> I did what would keep it from being profaned in the eyes of the nations in whose sight I had brought them out.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Also with uplifted hand I swore to them in the wilderness that I would disperse them among the nations and scatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20919BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20919BA\"></sup> them through the countries,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>because they had not obeyed my laws but had rejected my decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20920BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20920BB\"></sup> and desecrated my Sabbaths,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20920BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20920BC\"></sup> and their eyes lusted after<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20920BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20920BD\"></sup> their parents’ idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20920BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20920BE\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So I gave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20921BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20921BF\"></sup> them other statutes that were not good and laws through which they could not live;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20921BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20921BG\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I defiled them through their gifts—the sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20922BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20922BH\"></sup> of every firstborn—that I might fill them with horror so they would know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20922BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20922BI\"></sup>’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Therefore, son of man, speak to the people of Israel and say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: In this also your ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20923BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20923BJ\"></sup> blasphemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20923BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20923BK\"></sup> me by being unfaithful to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20923BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20923BL\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When I brought them into the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20924BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20924BM\"></sup> I had sworn to give them and they saw any high hill or any leafy tree, there they offered their sacrifices, made offerings that aroused my anger, presented their fragrant incense and poured out their drink offerings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20924BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20924BN\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then I said to them: What is this high place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20925BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20925BO\"></sup> you go to?’” (It is called Bamah to this day.)",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Therefore say to the Israelites: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Will you defile yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20926BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20926BP\"></sup> the way your ancestors did and lust after their vile images?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20926BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20926BQ\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When you offer your gifts—the sacrifice of your children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20927BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20927BR\"></sup> in the fire—you continue to defile yourselves with all your idols to this day. Am I to let you inquire of me, you Israelites? As surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I will not let you inquire of me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20927BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20927BS\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“‘You say, “We want to be like the nations, like the peoples of the world, who serve wood and stone.” But what you have in mind will never happen.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>As surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I will reign over you with a mighty hand and an outstretched arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20929BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20929BT\"></sup> and with outpoured wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20929BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20929BU\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>I will bring you from the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20930BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20930BV\"></sup> and gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20930BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20930BW\"></sup> you from the countries where you have been scattered—with a mighty hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20930BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20930BX\"></sup> and an outstretched arm and with outpoured wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20930BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20930BY\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>I will bring you into the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20931BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20931BZ\"></sup> of the nations and there, face to face, I will execute judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20931CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20931CA\"></sup> upon you.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>As I judged your ancestors in the wilderness of the land of Egypt, so I will judge you, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20932CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20932CB\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I will take note of you as you pass under my rod,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20933CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20933CC\"></sup> and I will bring you into the bond of the covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20933CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20933CD\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>I will purge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20934CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20934CE\"></sup> you of those who revolt and rebel against me. Although I will bring them out of the land where they are living, yet they will not enter the land of Israel. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20934CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20934CF\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“‘As for you, people of Israel, this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Go and serve your idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20935CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20935CG\"></sup> every one of you! But afterward you will surely listen to me and no longer profane my holy name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20935CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20935CH\"></sup> with your gifts and idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20935CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20935CI\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For on my holy mountain, the high mountain of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20936CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20936CJ\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, there in the land all the people of Israel will serve me, and there I will accept them. There I will require your offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20936CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20936CK\"></sup> and your choice gifts, along with all your holy sacrifices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20936CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20936CL\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>I will accept you as fragrant incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20937CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20937CM\"></sup> when I bring you out from the nations and gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20937CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20937CN\"></sup> you from the countries where you have been scattered, and I will be proved holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20937CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20937CO\"></sup> through you in the sight of the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20937CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20937CP\"></sup>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20938CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20938CQ\"></sup> when I bring you into the land of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20938CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20938CR\"></sup> the land I had sworn with uplifted hand to give to your ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20938CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20938CS\"></sup>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>There you will remember your conduct<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20939CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20939CT\"></sup> and all the actions by which you have defiled yourselves, and you will loathe yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20939CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20939CU\"></sup> for all the evil you have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20939CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20939CV\"></sup>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>You will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I deal with you for my name’s sake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20940CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20940CW\"></sup> and not according to your evil ways and your corrupt practices, you people of Israel, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20940CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20940CX\"></sup>’”",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>“Son of man, set your face toward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20942CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20942CY\"></sup> the south; preach against the south and prophesy against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20942CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20942CZ\"></sup> the forest of the southland.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20942DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20942DA\"></sup>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Say to the southern forest:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20943DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20943DB\"></sup> ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am about to set fire to you, and it will consume<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20943DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20943DC\"></sup> all your trees, both green and dry. The blazing flame will not be quenched, and every face from south to north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20943DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20943DD\"></sup> will be scorched by it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20943DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20943DE\"></sup>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Everyone will see that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have kindled it; it will not be quenched.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20944DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20944DF\"></sup>’”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Then I said, “Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20945DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20945DG\"></sup> they are saying of me, ‘Isn’t he just telling parables?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20945DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20945DH\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20946A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20946A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20947B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20947B\"></sup> Jerusalem and preach against the sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20947C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20947C\"></sup> Prophesy against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20947D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20947D\"></sup> the land of Israel",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say to her: ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20948E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20948E\"></sup> I will draw my sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20948F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20948F\"></sup> from its sheath and cut off from you both the righteous and the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20948G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20948G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Because I am going to cut off the righteous and the wicked, my sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20949H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20949H\"></sup> will be unsheathed against everyone from south to north.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20949I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20949I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then all people will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have drawn my sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20950J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20950J\"></sup> from its sheath; it will not return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20950K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20950K\"></sup> again.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20950L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20950L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Therefore groan, son of man! Groan before them with broken heart and bitter grief.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20951M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20951M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when they ask you, ‘Why are you groaning?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20952N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20952N\"></sup>’ you shall say, ‘Because of the news that is coming. Every heart will melt with fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20952O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20952O\"></sup> and every hand go limp;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20952P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20952P\"></sup> every spirit will become faint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20952Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20952Q\"></sup> and every leg will be wet with urine.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20952R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20952R\"></sup> It is coming! It will surely take place, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy and say, ‘This is what the Lord says:“‘A sword, a sword,sharpened and polished—",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>sharpened for the slaughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20955S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20955S\"></sup>polished to flash like lightning!“‘Shall we rejoice in the scepter of my royal son? The sword despises every such stick.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20955T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20955T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“‘The sword is appointed to be polished,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20956U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20956U\"></sup>to be grasped with the hand;it is sharpened and polished,made ready for the hand of the slayer.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Cry out and wail, son of man,for it is against my people;it is against all the princes of Israel.They are thrown to the swordalong with my people.Therefore beat your breast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20957V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20957V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘Testing will surely come. And what if even the scepter, which the sword despises, does not continue? declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“So then, son of man, prophesyand strike your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20959W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20959W\"></sup> together.Let the sword strike twice,even three times.It is a sword for slaughter—a sword for great slaughter,closing in on them from every side.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20959X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20959X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So that hearts may melt with fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20960Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20960Y\"></sup>and the fallen be many,I have stationed the sword for slaughterat all their gates.Look! It is forged to strike like lightning,it is grasped for slaughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20960Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20960Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Slash to the right, you sword,then to the left,wherever your blade is turned.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I too will strike my hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20962AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20962AA\"></sup> together,and my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20962AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20962AB\"></sup> will subside.I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20962AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20962AC\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Son of man, mark out two roads for the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20964AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20964AD\"></sup> of the king of Babylon to take, both starting from the same country. Make a signpost<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20964AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20964AE\"></sup> where the road branches off to the city.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Mark out one road for the sword to come against Rabbah of the Ammonites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20965AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20965AF\"></sup> and another against Judah and fortified Jerusalem.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the king of Babylon will stop at the fork in the road, at the junction of the two roads, to seek an omen: He will cast lots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20966AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20966AG\"></sup> with arrows, he will consult his idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20966AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20966AH\"></sup> he will examine the liver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20966AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20966AI\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Into his right hand will come the lot for Jerusalem, where he is to set up battering rams, to give the command to slaughter, to sound the battle cry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20967AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20967AJ\"></sup> to set battering rams against the gates, to build a ramp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20967AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20967AK\"></sup> and to erect siege works.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20967AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20967AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>It will seem like a false omen to those who have sworn allegiance to him, but he will remind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20968AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20968AM\"></sup> them of their guilt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20968AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20968AN\"></sup> and take them captive.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘Because you people have brought to mind your guilt by your open rebellion, revealing your sins in all that you do—because you have done this, you will be taken captive.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“‘You profane and wicked prince of Israel, whose day has come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20970AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20970AO\"></sup> whose time of punishment has reached its climax,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20970AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20970AP\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Take off the turban, remove the crown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20971AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20971AQ\"></sup> It will not be as it was: The lowly will be exalted and the exalted will be brought low.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20971AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20971AR\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>A ruin! A ruin! I will make it a ruin! The crown will not be restored until he to whom it rightfully belongs shall come;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20972AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20972AS\"></sup> to him I will give it.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20972AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20972AT\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“And you, son of man, prophesy and say, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about the Ammonites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20973AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20973AU\"></sup> and their insults:“‘A sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20973AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20973AV\"></sup> a sword,drawn for the slaughter,polished to consumeand to flash like lightning!",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Despite false visions concerning youand lying divinations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20974AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20974AW\"></sup> about you,it will be laid on the necksof the wicked who are to be slain,whose day has come,whose time of punishment has reached its climax.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20974AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20974AX\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“‘Let the sword return to its sheath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20975AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20975AY\"></sup>In the place where you were created,in the land of your ancestry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20975AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20975AZ\"></sup>I will judge you.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I will pour out my wrath on youand breathe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20976BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20976BA\"></sup> out my fiery anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20976BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20976BB\"></sup> against you;I will deliver you into the hands of brutal men,men skilled in destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20976BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20976BC\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>You will be fuel for the fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20977BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20977BD\"></sup>your blood will be shed in your land,you will be remembered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20977BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20977BE\"></sup> no more;for I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.’”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, will you judge her? Will you judge this city of bloodshed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20979A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20979A\"></sup> Then confront her with all her detestable practices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20979B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20979B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You city that brings on herself doom by shedding blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20980C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20980C\"></sup> in her midst and defiles herself by making idols,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>you have become guilty because of the blood you have shed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20981D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20981D\"></sup> and have become defiled by the idols you have made. You have brought your days to a close, and the end of your years has come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20981E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20981E\"></sup> Therefore I will make you an object of scorn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20981F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20981F\"></sup> to the nations and a laughingstock to all the countries.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20981G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20981G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who are near and those who are far away will mock you, you infamous city, full of turmoil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20982H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20982H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘See how each of the princes of Israel who are in you uses his power to shed blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20983I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20983I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In you they have treated father and mother with contempt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20984J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20984J\"></sup> in you they have oppressed the foreigner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20984K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20984K\"></sup> and mistreated the fatherless and the widow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20984L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20984L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You have despised my holy things and desecrated my Sabbaths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20985M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20985M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In you are slanderers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20986N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20986N\"></sup> who are bent on shedding blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20986O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20986O\"></sup> in you are those who eat at the mountain shrines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20986P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20986P\"></sup> and commit lewd acts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20986Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20986Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In you are those who dishonor their father’s bed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20987R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20987R\"></sup> in you are those who violate women during their period,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20987S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20987S\"></sup> when they are ceremonially unclean.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20987T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20987T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In you one man commits a detestable offense with his neighbor’s wife,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20988U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20988U\"></sup> another shamefully defiles his daughter-in-law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20988V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20988V\"></sup> and another violates his sister,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20988W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20988W\"></sup> his own father’s daughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20988X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20988X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In you are people who accept bribes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20989Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20989Y\"></sup> to shed blood; you take interest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20989Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20989Z\"></sup> and make a profit from the poor. You extort unjust gain from your neighbors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20989AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20989AA\"></sup> And you have forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20989AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20989AB\"></sup> me, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20989AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20989AC\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘I will surely strike my hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20990AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20990AD\"></sup> together at the unjust gain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20990AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20990AE\"></sup> you have made and at the blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20990AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20990AF\"></sup> you have shed in your midst.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20990AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20990AG\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Will your courage endure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20991AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20991AH\"></sup> or your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20991AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20991AI\"></sup> be strong in the day I deal with you? I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20991AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20991AJ\"></sup> and I will do it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20991AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20991AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will disperse you among the nations and scatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20992AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20992AL\"></sup> you through the countries; and I will put an end to<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20992AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20992AM\"></sup> your uncleanness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20992AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20992AN\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When you have been defiled in the eyes of the nations, you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, the people of Israel have become dross<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20995AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20995AO\"></sup> to me; all of them are the copper, tin, iron and lead left inside a furnace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20995AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20995AP\"></sup> They are but the dross of silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20995AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20995AQ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘Because you have all become dross,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20996AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20996AR\"></sup> I will gather you into Jerusalem.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As silver, copper, iron, lead and tin are gathered into a furnace to be melted with a fiery blast, so will I gather you in my anger and my wrath and put you inside the city and melt you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20997AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20997AS\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will gather you and I will blow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20998AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20998AT\"></sup> on you with my fiery wrath, and you will be melted inside her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20998AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20998AU\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>As silver is melted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20999AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20999AV\"></sup> in a furnace, so you will be melted inside her, and you will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have poured out my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20999AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20999AW\"></sup> on you.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20999AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20999AX\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Again the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Son of man, say to the land, ‘You are a land that has not been cleansed or rained on in the day of wrath.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21001AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21001AY\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>There is a conspiracy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21002AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21002AZ\"></sup> of her princes within her like a roaring lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21002BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21002BA\"></sup> tearing its prey; they devour people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21002BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21002BB\"></sup> take treasures and precious things and make many widows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21002BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21002BC\"></sup> within her.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Her priests do violence to my law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21003BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21003BD\"></sup> and profane my holy things; they do not distinguish between the holy and the common;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21003BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21003BE\"></sup> they teach that there is no difference between the unclean and the clean;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21003BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21003BF\"></sup> and they shut their eyes to the keeping of my Sabbaths, so that I am profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21003BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21003BG\"></sup> among them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21003BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21003BH\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Her officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21004BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21004BI\"></sup> within her are like wolves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21004BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21004BJ\"></sup> tearing their prey; they shed blood and kill people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21004BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21004BK\"></sup> to make unjust gain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21004BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21004BL\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Her prophets whitewash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21005BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21005BM\"></sup> these deeds for them by false visions and lying divinations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21005BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21005BN\"></sup> They say, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says’—when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21005BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21005BO\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The people of the land practice extortion and commit robbery;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21006BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21006BP\"></sup> they oppress the poor and needy and mistreat the foreigner,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21006BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21006BQ\"></sup> denying them justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21006BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21006BR\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“I looked for someone among them who would build up the wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21007BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21007BS\"></sup> and stand before me in the gap on behalf of the land so I would not have to destroy it, but I found no one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21007BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21007BT\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So I will pour out my wrath on them and consume them with my fiery anger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21008BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21008BU\"></sup> bringing down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21008BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21008BV\"></sup> on their own heads all they have done, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21008BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21008BW\"></sup>”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, there were two women, daughters of the same mother.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21010A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21010A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They became prostitutes in Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21011B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21011B\"></sup> engaging in prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21011C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21011C\"></sup> from their youth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21011D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21011D\"></sup> In that land their breasts were fondled and their virgin bosoms caressed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21011E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21011E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The older was named Oholah, and her sister was Oholibah. They were mine and gave birth to sons and daughters. Oholah is Samaria, and Oholibah is Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21012F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21012F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Oholah engaged in prostitution while she was still mine; and she lusted after her lovers, the Assyrians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21013G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21013G\"></sup>—warriors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21013H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21013H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>clothed in blue, governors and commanders, all of them handsome young men, and mounted horsemen.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>She gave herself as a prostitute to all the elite of the Assyrians and defiled herself with all the idols of everyone she lusted after.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21015I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21015I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>She did not give up the prostitution she began in Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21016J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21016J\"></sup> when during her youth men slept with her, caressed her virgin bosom and poured out their lust on her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21016K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21016K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Therefore I delivered her into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21017L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21017L\"></sup> of her lovers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21017M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21017M\"></sup> the Assyrians, for whom she lusted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21017N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21017N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They stripped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21018O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21018O\"></sup> her naked, took away her sons and daughters and killed her with the sword. She became a byword among women,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21018P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21018P\"></sup> and punishment was inflicted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21018Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21018Q\"></sup> on her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21018R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21018R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Her sister Oholibah saw this,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21019S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21019S\"></sup> yet in her lust and prostitution she was more depraved than her sister.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21019T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21019T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>She too lusted after the Assyrians—governors and commanders, warriors in full dress, mounted horsemen, all handsome young men.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21020U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21020U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I saw that she too defiled herself; both of them went the same way.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21021V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21021V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“But she carried her prostitution still further. She saw men portrayed on a wall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21022W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21022W\"></sup> figures of Chaldeans portrayed in red,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21022X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21022X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>with belts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21023Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21023Y\"></sup> around their waists and flowing turbans on their heads; all of them looked like Babylonian chariot officers, natives of Chaldea.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>As soon as she saw them, she lusted after them and sent messengers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21024Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21024Z\"></sup> to them in Chaldea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21024AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21024AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then the Babylonians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21025AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21025AB\"></sup> came to her, to the bed of love, and in their lust they defiled her. After she had been defiled by them, she turned away from them in disgust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21025AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21025AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When she carried on her prostitution openly and exposed her naked body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21026AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21026AD\"></sup> I turned away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21026AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21026AE\"></sup> from her in disgust, just as I had turned away from her sister.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21026AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21026AF\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Yet she became more and more promiscuous as she recalled the days of her youth, when she was a prostitute in Egypt.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>There she lusted after her lovers, whose genitals were like those of donkeys and whose emission was like that of horses.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So you longed for the lewdness of your youth, when in Egypt your bosom was caressed and your young breasts fondled.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21029AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21029AG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Therefore, Oholibah, this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will stir up your lovers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21030AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21030AH\"></sup> against you, those you turned away from in disgust, and I will bring them against you from every side<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21030AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21030AI\"></sup>—",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>the Babylonians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21031AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21031AJ\"></sup> and all the Chaldeans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21031AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21031AK\"></sup> the men of Pekod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21031AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21031AL\"></sup> and Shoa and Koa, and all the Assyrians with them, handsome young men, all of them governors and commanders, chariot officers and men of high rank, all mounted on horses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21031AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21031AM\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They will come against you with weapons, chariots and wagons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21032AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21032AN\"></sup> and with a throng of people; they will take up positions against you on every side with large and small shields and with helmets. I will turn you over to them for punishment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21032AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21032AO\"></sup> and they will punish you according to their standards.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will direct my jealous anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21033AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21033AP\"></sup> against you, and they will deal with you in fury. They will cut off your noses and your ears, and those of you who are left will fall by the sword. They will take away your sons and daughters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21033AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21033AQ\"></sup> and those of you who are left will be consumed by fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21033AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21033AR\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will also strip<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21034AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21034AS\"></sup> you of your clothes and take your fine jewelry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21034AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21034AT\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So I will put a stop<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21035AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21035AU\"></sup> to the lewdness and prostitution you began in Egypt. You will not look on these things with longing or remember Egypt anymore.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am about to deliver you into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21036AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21036AV\"></sup> of those you hate, to those you turned away from in disgust.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>They will deal with you in hatred and take away everything you have worked for. They will leave you stark naked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21037AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21037AW\"></sup> and the shame of your prostitution will be exposed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21037AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21037AX\"></sup> Your lewdness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21037AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21037AY\"></sup> and promiscuity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21037AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21037AZ\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>have brought this on you, because you lusted after the nations and defiled yourself with their idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21038BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21038BA\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>You have gone the way of your sister; so I will put her cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21039BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21039BB\"></sup> into your hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21039BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21039BC\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“You will drink your sister’s cup,a cup large and deep;it will bring scorn and derision,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21040BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21040BD\"></sup>for it holds so much.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21040BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21040BE\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>You will be filled with drunkenness and sorrow,the cup of ruin and desolation,the cup of your sister Samaria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21041BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21041BF\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>You will drink it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21042BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21042BG\"></sup> and drain it dryand chew on its pieces—and you will tear your breasts.I have spoken, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21042BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21042BH\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Since you have forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21043BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21043BI\"></sup> me and turned your back on me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21043BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21043BJ\"></sup> you must bear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21043BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21043BK\"></sup> the consequences of your lewdness and prostitution.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: “Son of man, will you judge Oholah and Oholibah? Then confront<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21044BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21044BL\"></sup> them with their detestable practices,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21044BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21044BM\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>for they have committed adultery and blood is on their hands. They committed adultery with their idols; they even sacrificed their children, whom they bore to me, as food for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21045BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21045BN\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>They have also done this to me: At that same time they defiled my sanctuary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21046BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21046BO\"></sup> and desecrated my Sabbaths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21046BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21046BP\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>On the very day they sacrificed their children to their idols, they entered my sanctuary and desecrated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21047BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21047BQ\"></sup> it. That is what they did in my house.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21047BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21047BR\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>“They even sent messengers for men who came from far away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21048BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21048BS\"></sup> and when they arrived you bathed yourself for them, applied eye makeup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21048BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21048BT\"></sup> and put on your jewelry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21048BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21048BU\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>You sat on an elegant couch,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21049BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21049BV\"></sup> with a table<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21049BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21049BW\"></sup> spread before it on which you had placed the incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21049BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21049BX\"></sup> and olive oil that belonged to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21049BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21049BY\"></sup>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“The noise of a carefree<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21050BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21050BZ\"></sup> crowd was around her; drunkards<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21050CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21050CA\"></sup> were brought from the desert along with men from the rabble, and they put bracelets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21050CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21050CB\"></sup> on the wrists of the woman and her sister and beautiful crowns on their heads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21050CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21050CC\"></sup>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Then I said about the one worn out by adultery, ‘Now let them use her as a prostitute,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21051CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21051CD\"></sup> for that is all she is.’",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And they slept with her. As men sleep with a prostitute, so they slept with those lewd women, Oholah and Oholibah.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>But righteous judges will sentence them to the punishment of women who commit adultery and shed blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21053CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21053CE\"></sup> because they are adulterous and blood is on their hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21053CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21053CF\"></sup>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Bring a mob<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21054CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21054CG\"></sup> against them and give them over to terror and plunder.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21054CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21054CH\"></sup>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>The mob will stone them and cut them down with their swords; they will kill their sons and daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21055CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21055CI\"></sup> and burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21055CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21055CJ\"></sup> down their houses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21055CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21055CK\"></sup>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>“So I will put an end<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21056CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21056CL\"></sup> to lewdness in the land, that all women may take warning and not imitate you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21056CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21056CM\"></sup>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>You will suffer the penalty for your lewdness and bear the consequences of your sins of idolatry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21057CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21057CN\"></sup> Then you will know that I am the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21057CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21057CO\"></sup>”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>In the ninth year, in the tenth month on the tenth day, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21058A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21058A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, record<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21059B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21059B\"></sup> this date, this very date, because the king of Babylon has laid siege to Jerusalem this very day.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21059C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21059C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Tell this rebellious people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21060D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21060D\"></sup> a parable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21060E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21060E\"></sup> and say to them: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Put on the cooking pot;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21060F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21060F\"></sup> put it onand pour water into it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Put into it the pieces of meat,all the choice pieces—the leg and the shoulder.Fill it with the best of these bones;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21061G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21061G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>take the pick of the flock.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21062H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21062H\"></sup>Pile wood beneath it for the bones;bring it to a boiland cook the bones in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21062I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21062I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21063J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21063J\"></sup> to the city of bloodshed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21063K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21063K\"></sup>to the pot now encrusted,whose deposit will not go away!Take the meat out piece by piecein whatever order<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21063L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21063L\"></sup> it comes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21063M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21063M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘For the blood she shed is in her midst:She poured it on the bare rock;she did not pour it on the ground,where the dust would cover it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21064N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21064N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>To stir up wrath and take revengeI put her blood on the bare rock,so that it would not be covered.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Woe to the city of bloodshed!I, too, will pile the wood high.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So heap on the woodand kindle the fire.Cook the meat well,mixing in the spices;and let the bones be charred.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then set the empty pot on the coalstill it becomes hot and its copper glows,so that its impurities may be meltedand its deposit burned away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21068O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21068O\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It has frustrated all efforts;its heavy deposit has not been removed,not even by fire.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘Now your impurity is lewdness. Because I tried to cleanse you but you would not be cleansed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21070P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21070P\"></sup> from your impurity, you will not be clean again until my wrath against you has subsided.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21070Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21070Q\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“‘I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21071R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21071R\"></sup> The time has come for me to act.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21071S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21071S\"></sup> I will not hold back; I will not have pity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21071T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21071T\"></sup> nor will I relent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21071U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21071U\"></sup> You will be judged according to your conduct and your actions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21071V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21071V\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21071W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21071W\"></sup>’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Son of man, with one blow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21073X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21073X\"></sup> I am about to take away from you the delight of your eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21073Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21073Y\"></sup> Yet do not lament or weep or shed any tears.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21073Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21073Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Groan quietly;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21074AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21074AA\"></sup> do not mourn for the dead. Keep your turban<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21074AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21074AB\"></sup> fastened and your sandals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21074AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21074AC\"></sup> on your feet; do not cover your mustache and beard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21074AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21074AD\"></sup> or eat the customary food of mourners.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21074AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21074AE\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So I spoke to the people in the morning, and in the evening my wife died. The next morning I did as I had been commanded.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21075AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21075AF\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the people asked me, “Won’t you tell us what these things have to do with us?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21076AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21076AG\"></sup> Why are you acting like this?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So I said to them, “The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Say to the people of Israel, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am about to desecrate my sanctuary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21078AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21078AH\"></sup>—the stronghold in which you take pride,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21078AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21078AI\"></sup> the delight of your eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21078AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21078AJ\"></sup> the object of your affection. The sons and daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21078AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21078AK\"></sup> you left behind will fall by the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21078AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21078AL\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And you will do as I have done. You will not cover your mustache and beard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21079AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21079AM\"></sup> or eat the customary food of mourners.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21079AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21079AN\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>You will keep your turbans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21080AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21080AO\"></sup> on your heads and your sandals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21080AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21080AP\"></sup> on your feet. You will not mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21080AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21080AQ\"></sup> or weep but will waste away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21080AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21080AR\"></sup> because of your sins and groan among yourselves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21080AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21080AS\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Ezekiel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21081AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21081AT\"></sup> will be a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21081AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21081AU\"></sup> to you; you will do just as he has done. When this happens, you will know that I am the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“And you, son of man, on the day I take away their stronghold, their joy and glory, the delight of their eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21082AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21082AV\"></sup> their heart’s desire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21082AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21082AW\"></sup> and their sons and daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21082AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21082AX\"></sup> as well—",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>on that day a fugitive will come to tell you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21083AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21083AY\"></sup> the news.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>At that time your mouth will be opened; you will speak with him and will no longer be silent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21084AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21084AZ\"></sup> So you will be a sign to them, and they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21084BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21084BA\"></sup>”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21086A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21086A\"></sup> the Ammonites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21086B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21086B\"></sup> and prophesy against them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21086C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21086C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Say to them, ‘Hear the word of the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Because you said “Aha!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21087D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21087D\"></sup>” over my sanctuary when it was desecrated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21087E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21087E\"></sup> and over the land of Israel when it was laid waste and over the people of Judah when they went into exile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21087F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21087F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>therefore I am going to give you to the people of the East<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21088G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21088G\"></sup> as a possession. They will set up their camps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21088H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21088H\"></sup> and pitch their tents among you; they will eat your fruit and drink your milk.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21088I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21088I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will turn Rabbah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21089J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21089J\"></sup> into a pasture for camels and Ammon into a resting place for sheep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21089K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21089K\"></sup> Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Because you have clapped your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21090L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21090L\"></sup> and stamped your feet, rejoicing with all the malice of your heart against the land of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21090M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21090M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>therefore I will stretch out my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21091N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21091N\"></sup> against you and give you as plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21091O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21091O\"></sup> to the nations. I will wipe you out from among the nations and exterminate you from the countries. I will destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21091P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21091P\"></sup> you, and you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21091Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21091Q\"></sup>’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘Because Moab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21092R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21092R\"></sup> and Seir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21092S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21092S\"></sup> said, “Look, Judah has become like all the other nations,”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>therefore I will expose the flank of Moab, beginning at its frontier towns—Beth Jeshimoth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21093T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21093T\"></sup>, Baal Meon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21093U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21093U\"></sup> and Kiriathaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21093V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21093V\"></sup>—the glory of that land.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will give Moab along with the Ammonites to the people of the East as a possession, so that the Ammonites will not be remembered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21094W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21094W\"></sup> among the nations;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and I will inflict punishment on Moab. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21095X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21095X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘Because Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21096Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21096Y\"></sup> took revenge on Judah and became very guilty by doing so,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will stretch out my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21097Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21097Z\"></sup> against Edom and kill both man and beast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21097AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21097AA\"></sup> I will lay it waste, and from Teman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21097AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21097AB\"></sup> to Dedan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21097AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21097AC\"></sup> they will fall by the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21097AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21097AD\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will take vengeance on Edom by the hand of my people Israel, and they will deal with Edom in accordance with my anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21098AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21098AE\"></sup> and my wrath; they will know my vengeance, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21098AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21098AF\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘Because the Philistines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21099AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21099AG\"></sup> acted in vengeance and took revenge with malice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21099AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21099AH\"></sup> in their hearts, and with ancient hostility sought to destroy Judah,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am about to stretch out my hand against the Philistines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21100AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21100AI\"></sup> and I will wipe out the Kerethites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21100AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21100AJ\"></sup> and destroy those remaining along the coast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21100AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21100AK\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will carry out great vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21101AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21101AL\"></sup> on them and punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21101AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21101AM\"></sup> them in my wrath. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21101AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21101AN\"></sup> when I take vengeance on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21101AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21101AO\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>In the eleventh month of the twelfth year, on the first day of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21102A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21102A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, because Tyre<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21103B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21103B\"></sup> has said of Jerusalem, ‘Aha!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21103C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21103C\"></sup> The gate to the nations is broken, and its doors have swung open to me; now that she lies in ruins I will prosper,’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against you, Tyre, and I will bring many nations against you, like the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21104D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21104D\"></sup> casting up its waves.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21105E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21105E\"></sup> the walls of Tyre<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21105F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21105F\"></sup> and pull down her towers; I will scrape away her rubble and make her a bare rock.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Out in the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21106G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21106G\"></sup> she will become a place to spread fishnets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21106H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21106H\"></sup> for I have spoken, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. She will become plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21106I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21106I\"></sup> for the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21106J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21106J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and her settlements on the mainland will be ravaged by the sword. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: From the north I am going to bring against Tyre Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21108K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21108K\"></sup> king of Babylon, king of kings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21108L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21108L\"></sup> with horses and chariots,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21108M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21108M\"></sup> with horsemen and a great army.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He will ravage your settlements on the mainland with the sword; he will set up siege works<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21109N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21109N\"></sup> against you, build a ramp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21109O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21109O\"></sup> up to your walls and raise his shields against you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He will direct the blows of his battering rams against your walls and demolish your towers with his weapons.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21110P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21110P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>His horses will be so many that they will cover you with dust. Your walls will tremble at the noise of the warhorses, wagons and chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21111Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21111Q\"></sup> when he enters your gates as men enter a city whose walls have been broken through.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The hooves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21112R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21112R\"></sup> of his horses will trample all your streets; he will kill your people with the sword, and your strong pillars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21112S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21112S\"></sup> will fall to the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21112T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21112T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They will plunder your wealth and loot your merchandise; they will break down your walls and demolish your fine houses and throw your stones, timber and rubble into the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21113U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21113U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will put an end<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21114V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21114V\"></sup> to your noisy songs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21114W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21114W\"></sup> and the music of your harps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21114X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21114X\"></sup> will be heard no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21114Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21114Y\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will make you a bare rock, and you will become a place to spread fishnets. You will never be rebuilt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21115Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21115Z\"></sup> for I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to Tyre: Will not the coastlands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21116AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21116AA\"></sup> tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21116AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21116AB\"></sup> at the sound of your fall, when the wounded groan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21116AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21116AC\"></sup> and the slaughter takes place in you?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then all the princes of the coast will step down from their thrones and lay aside their robes and take off their embroidered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21117AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21117AD\"></sup> garments. Clothed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21117AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21117AE\"></sup> with terror, they will sit on the ground,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21117AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21117AF\"></sup> trembling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21117AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21117AG\"></sup> every moment, appalled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21117AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21117AH\"></sup> at you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then they will take up a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21118AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21118AI\"></sup> concerning you and say to you:“‘How you are destroyed, city of renown,peopled by men of the sea!You were a power on the seas,you and your citizens;you put your terroron all who lived there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21118AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21118AJ\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now the coastlands tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21119AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21119AK\"></sup>on the day of your fall;the islands in the seaare terrified at your collapse.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21119AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21119AL\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: When I make you a desolate city, like cities no longer inhabited, and when I bring the ocean depths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21120AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21120AM\"></sup> over you and its vast waters cover you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21120AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21120AN\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>then I will bring you down with those who go down to the pit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21121AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21121AO\"></sup> to the people of long ago. I will make you dwell in the earth below, as in ancient ruins, with those who go down to the pit, and you will not return or take your place in the land of the living.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21121AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21121AP\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will bring you to a horrible end and you will be no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21122AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21122AQ\"></sup> You will be sought, but you will never again be found, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21122AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21122AR\"></sup>"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, take up a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21124A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21124A\"></sup> concerning Tyre.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Say to Tyre,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21125B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21125B\"></sup> situated at the gateway to the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21125C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21125C\"></sup> merchant of peoples on many coasts, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘You say, Tyre,“I am perfect in beauty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21125D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21125D\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your domain was on the high seas;your builders brought your beauty to perfection.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21126E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21126E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They made all your timbersof juniper from Senir;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21127F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21127F\"></sup>they took a cedar from Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21127G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21127G\"></sup>to make a mast for you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Of oaks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21128H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21128H\"></sup> from Bashanthey made your oars;of cypress wood from the coasts of Cyprus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21128I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21128I\"></sup>they made your deck, adorned with ivory.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Fine embroidered linen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21129J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21129J\"></sup> from Egypt was your sailand served as your banner;your awnings were of blue and purple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21129K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21129K\"></sup>from the coasts of Elishah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21129L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21129L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Men of Sidon and Arvad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21130M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21130M\"></sup> were your oarsmen;your skilled men, Tyre, were aboard as your sailors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21130N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21130N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Veteran craftsmen of Byblos<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21131O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21131O\"></sup> were on boardas shipwrights to caulk your seams.All the ships of the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21131P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21131P\"></sup> and their sailorscame alongside to trade for your wares.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘Men of Persia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21132Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21132Q\"></sup> Lydia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21132R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21132R\"></sup> and Put<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21132S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21132S\"></sup>served as soldiers in your army.They hung their shields<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21132T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21132T\"></sup> and helmets on your walls,bringing you splendor.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Men of Arvad and Helekguarded your walls on every side;men of Gammadwere in your towers.They hung their shields around your walls;they brought your beauty to perfection.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21133U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21133U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“‘Tarshish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21134V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21134V\"></sup> did business with you because of your great wealth of goods;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21134W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21134W\"></sup> they exchanged silver, iron, tin and lead for your merchandise.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘Greece,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21135X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21135X\"></sup> Tubal and Meshek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21135Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21135Y\"></sup> did business with you; they traded human beings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21135Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21135Z\"></sup> and articles of bronze for your wares.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“‘Men of Beth Togarmah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21136AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21136AA\"></sup> exchanged chariot horses, cavalry horses and mules for your merchandise.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“‘The men of Rhodes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21137AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21137AB\"></sup> traded with you, and many coastlands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21137AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21137AC\"></sup> were your customers; they paid you with ivory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21137AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21137AD\"></sup> tusks and ebony.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“‘Aram<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21138AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21138AE\"></sup> did business with you because of your many products; they exchanged turquoise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21138AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21138AF\"></sup> purple fabric, embroidered work, fine linen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21138AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21138AG\"></sup> coral<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21138AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21138AH\"></sup> and rubies for your merchandise.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“‘Judah and Israel traded with you; they exchanged wheat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21139AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21139AI\"></sup> from Minnith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21139AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21139AJ\"></sup> and confections, honey, olive oil and balm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21139AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21139AK\"></sup> for your wares.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21139AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21139AL\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“‘Damascus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21140AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21140AM\"></sup> did business with you because of your many products and great wealth of goods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21140AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21140AN\"></sup> They offered wine from Helbon, wool from Zahar",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and casks of wine from Izal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21141AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21141AO\"></sup> in exchange for your wares: wrought iron, cassia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21141AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21141AP\"></sup> and calamus.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“‘Dedan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21142AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21142AQ\"></sup> traded in saddle blankets with you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“‘Arabia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21143AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21143AR\"></sup> and all the princes of Kedar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21143AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21143AS\"></sup> were your customers; they did business with you in lambs, rams and goats.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“‘The merchants of Sheba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21144AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21144AT\"></sup> and Raamah traded with you; for your merchandise they exchanged the finest of all kinds of spices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21144AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21144AU\"></sup> and precious stones, and gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21144AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21144AV\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“‘Harran,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21145AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21145AW\"></sup> Kanneh and Eden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21145AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21145AX\"></sup> and merchants of Sheba, Ashur<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21145AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21145AY\"></sup> and Kilmad traded with you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>In your marketplace they traded with you beautiful garments, blue fabric, embroidered work and multicolored rugs with cords twisted and tightly knotted.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“‘The ships of Tarshish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21147AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21147AZ\"></sup> serveas carriers for your wares.You are filled with heavy cargoas you sail the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21147BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21147BA\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Your oarsmen take youout to the high seas.But the east wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21148BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21148BB\"></sup> will break you to piecesfar out at sea.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Your wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21149BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21149BC\"></sup> merchandise and wares,your mariners, sailors and shipwrights,your merchants and all your soldiers,and everyone else on boardwill sink into the heart of the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21149BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21149BD\"></sup>on the day of your shipwreck.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The shorelands will quake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21150BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21150BE\"></sup>when your sailors cry out.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>All who handle the oarswill abandon their ships;the mariners and all the sailorswill stand on the shore.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>They will raise their voiceand cry bitterly over you;they will sprinkle dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21152BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21152BF\"></sup> on their headsand roll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21152BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21152BG\"></sup> in ashes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21152BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21152BH\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>They will shave their heads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21153BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21153BI\"></sup> because of youand will put on sackcloth.They will weep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21153BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21153BJ\"></sup> over you with anguish of souland with bitter mourning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21153BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21153BK\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>As they wail and mourn over you,they will take up a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21154BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21154BL\"></sup> concerning you:“Who was ever silenced like Tyre,surrounded by the sea?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21154BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21154BM\"></sup>”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>When your merchandise went out on the seas,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21155BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21155BN\"></sup>you satisfied many nations;with your great wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21155BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21155BO\"></sup> and your waresyou enriched the kings of the earth.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Now you are shattered by the seain the depths of the waters;your wares and all your companyhave gone down with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21156BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21156BP\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>All who live in the coastlands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21157BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21157BQ\"></sup>are appalled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21157BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21157BR\"></sup> at you;their kings shudder with horrorand their faces are distorted with fear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21157BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21157BS\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>The merchants among the nations scoff at you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21158BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21158BT\"></sup>you have come to a horrible endand will be no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21158BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21158BU\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21160A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21160A\"></sup>, say to the ruler of Tyre, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘In the pride of your heartyou say, “I am a god;I sit on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21160B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21160B\"></sup> of a godin the heart of the seas.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21160C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21160C\"></sup>But you are a mere mortal and not a god,though you think you are as wise as a god.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21160D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21160D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Are you wiser than Daniel?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21161E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21161E\"></sup>Is no secret hidden from you?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>By your wisdom and understandingyou have gained wealth for yourselfand amassed gold and silverin your treasuries.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21162F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21162F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>By your great skill in trading<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21163G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21163G\"></sup>you have increased your wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21163H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21163H\"></sup>and because of your wealthyour heart has grown proud.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21163I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21163I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Because you think you are wise,as wise as a god,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I am going to bring foreigners against you,the most ruthless of nations;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21165J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21165J\"></sup>they will draw their swords against your beauty and wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21165K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21165K\"></sup>and pierce your shining splendor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21165L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21165L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They will bring you down to the pit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21166M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21166M\"></sup>and you will die a violent death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21166N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21166N\"></sup>in the heart of the seas.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21166O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21166O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Will you then say, “I am a god,”in the presence of those who kill you?You will be but a mortal, not a god,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21167P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21167P\"></sup>in the hands of those who slay you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21167Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21167Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You will die the death of the uncircumcised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21168R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21168R\"></sup>at the hands of foreigners.I have spoken, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Son of man, take up a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21170S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21170S\"></sup> concerning the king of Tyre and say to him: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘You were the seal of perfection,full of wisdom and perfect in beauty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21170T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21170T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You were in Eden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21171U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21171U\"></sup>the garden of God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21171V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21171V\"></sup>every precious stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21171W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21171W\"></sup> adorned you:carnelian, chrysolite and emerald,topaz, onyx and jasper,lapis lazuli, turquoise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21171X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21171X\"></sup> and beryl.Your settings and mountings were made of gold;on the day you were created they were prepared.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21171Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21171Y\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You were anointed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21172Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21172Z\"></sup> as a guardian cherub,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21172AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21172AA\"></sup>for so I ordained you.You were on the holy mount of God;you walked among the fiery stones.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You were blameless in your waysfrom the day you were createdtill wickedness was found in you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Through your widespread tradeyou were filled with violence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21174AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21174AB\"></sup>and you sinned.So I drove you in disgrace from the mount of God,and I expelled you, guardian cherub,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21174AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21174AC\"></sup>from among the fiery stones.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Your heart became proud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21175AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21175AD\"></sup>on account of your beauty,and you corrupted your wisdombecause of your splendor.So I threw you to the earth;I made a spectacle of you before kings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21175AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21175AE\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>By your many sins and dishonest tradeyou have desecrated your sanctuaries.So I made a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21176AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21176AF\"></sup> come out from you,and it consumed you,and I reduced you to ashes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21176AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21176AG\"></sup> on the groundin the sight of all who were watching.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21176AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21176AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>All the nations who knew youare appalled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21177AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21177AI\"></sup> at you;you have come to a horrible endand will be no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21177AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21177AJ\"></sup>’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21179AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21179AK\"></sup> Sidon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21179AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21179AL\"></sup> prophesy against her",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘I am against you, Sidon,and among you I will display my glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21180AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21180AM\"></sup>You will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,when I inflict punishment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21180AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21180AN\"></sup> on youand within you am proved to be holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21180AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21180AO\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will send a plague upon youand make blood flow in your streets.The slain will fall within you,with the sword against you on every side.Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21181AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21181AP\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“‘No longer will the people of Israel have malicious neighbors who are painful briers and sharp thorns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21182AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21182AQ\"></sup> Then they will know that I am the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: When I gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21183AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21183AR\"></sup> the people of Israel from the nations where they have been scattered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21183AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21183AS\"></sup> I will be proved holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21183AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21183AT\"></sup> through them in the sight of the nations. Then they will live in their own land, which I gave to my servant Jacob.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21183AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21183AU\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will live there in safety<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21184AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21184AV\"></sup> and will build houses and plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21184AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21184AW\"></sup> vineyards; they will live in safety when I inflict punishment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21184AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21184AX\"></sup> on all their neighbors who maligned them. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21184AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21184AY\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>In the tenth year, in the tenth month on the twelfth day, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21185A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21185A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21186B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21186B\"></sup> Pharaoh king of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21186C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21186C\"></sup> and prophesy against him and against all Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21186D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21186D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Speak to him and say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘I am against you, Pharaoh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21187E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21187E\"></sup> king of Egypt,you great monster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21187F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21187F\"></sup> lying among your streams.You say, “The Nile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21187G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21187G\"></sup> belongs to me;I made it for myself.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But I will put hooks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21188H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21188H\"></sup> in your jawsand make the fish of your streams stick to your scales.I will pull you out from among your streams,with all the fish sticking to your scales.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21188I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21188I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will leave you in the desert,you and all the fish of your streams.You will fall on the open fieldand not be gathered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21189J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21189J\"></sup> or picked up.I will give you as foodto the beasts of the earth and the birds of the sky.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21189K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21189K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then all who live in Egypt will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“‘You have been a staff of reed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21190L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21190L\"></sup> for the people of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When they grasped you with their hands, you splintered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21191M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21191M\"></sup> and you tore open their shoulders; when they leaned on you, you broke and their backs were wrenched.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21191N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21191N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will bring a sword against you and kill both man and beast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21192O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21192O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Egypt will become a desolate wasteland. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“‘Because you said, “The Nile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21193P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21193P\"></sup> is mine; I made it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21193Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21193Q\"></sup>”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>therefore I am against you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21194R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21194R\"></sup> and against your streams, and I will make the land of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21194S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21194S\"></sup> a ruin and a desolate waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21194T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21194T\"></sup> from Migdol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21194U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21194U\"></sup> to Aswan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21194V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21194V\"></sup> as far as the border of Cush.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21194W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21194W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The foot of neither man nor beast will pass through it; no one will live there for forty years.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21195X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21195X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will make the land of Egypt desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21196Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21196Y\"></sup> among devastated lands, and her cities will lie desolate forty years among ruined cities. And I will disperse the Egyptians among the nations and scatter them through the countries.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21196Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21196Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘Yet this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: At the end of forty years I will gather the Egyptians from the nations where they were scattered.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will bring them back from captivity and return them to Upper Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21198AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21198AA\"></sup> the land of their ancestry. There they will be a lowly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21198AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21198AB\"></sup> kingdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21198AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21198AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>It will be the lowliest of kingdoms and will never again exalt itself above the other nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21199AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21199AD\"></sup> I will make it so weak that it will never again rule over the nations.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Egypt will no longer be a source of confidence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21200AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21200AE\"></sup> for the people of Israel but will be a reminder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21200AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21200AF\"></sup> of their sin in turning to her for help.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21200AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21200AG\"></sup> Then they will know that I am the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21200AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21200AH\"></sup>’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the twenty-seventh year, in the first month on the first day, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21201AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21201AI\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21202AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21202AJ\"></sup> king of Babylon drove his army in a hard campaign against Tyre; every head was rubbed bare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21202AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21202AK\"></sup> and every shoulder made raw.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21202AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21202AL\"></sup> Yet he and his army got no reward from the campaign he led against Tyre.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am going to give Egypt to Nebuchadnezzar king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21203AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21203AM\"></sup> of Babylon, and he will carry off its wealth. He will loot and plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21203AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21203AN\"></sup> the land as pay for his army.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21203AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21203AO\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I have given him Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21204AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21204AP\"></sup> as a reward for his efforts because he and his army did it for me, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21204AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21204AQ\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“On that day I will make a horn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21205AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21205AR\"></sup> grow for the Israelites, and I will open your mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21205AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21205AS\"></sup> among them. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21205AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21205AT\"></sup>”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy and say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Wail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21207A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21207A\"></sup> and say,“Alas for that day!”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the day is near,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21208B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21208B\"></sup>the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21208C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21208C\"></sup> is near—a day of clouds,a time of doom for the nations.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A sword will come against Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21209D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21209D\"></sup>and anguish will come upon Cush.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21209E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21209E\"></sup>When the slain fall in Egypt,her wealth will be carried awayand her foundations torn down.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21209F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21209F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Cush and Libya,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21210G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21210G\"></sup> Lydia and all Arabia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21210H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21210H\"></sup> Kub and the people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21210I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21210I\"></sup> of the covenant land will fall by the sword along with Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21210J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21210J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘The allies of Egypt will falland her proud strength will fail.From Migdol to Aswan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21211K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21211K\"></sup>they will fall by the sword within her,declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘They will be desolateamong desolate lands,and their cities will lieamong ruined cities.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21212L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21212L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,when I set fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21213M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21213M\"></sup> to Egyptand all her helpers are crushed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21213N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21213N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘On that day messengers will go out from me in ships to frighten Cush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21214O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21214O\"></sup> out of her complacency. Anguish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21214P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21214P\"></sup> will take hold of them on the day of Egypt’s doom, for it is sure to come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21214Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21214Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘I will put an end to the hordes of Egyptby the hand of Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21215R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21215R\"></sup> king of Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21215S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21215S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He and his army—the most ruthless of nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21216T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21216T\"></sup>—will be brought in to destroy the land.They will draw their swords against Egyptand fill the land with the slain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21216U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21216U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will dry up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21217V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21217V\"></sup> the waters of the Nile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21217W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21217W\"></sup>and sell the land to an evil nation;by the hand of foreignersI will lay waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21217X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21217X\"></sup> the land and everything in it.I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘I will destroy the idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21218Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21218Y\"></sup>and put an end to the images in Memphis.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21218Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21218Z\"></sup>No longer will there be a prince in Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21218AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21218AA\"></sup>and I will spread fear throughout the land.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will lay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21219AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21219AB\"></sup> waste Upper Egypt,set fire to Zoan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21219AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21219AC\"></sup>and inflict punishment on Thebes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21219AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21219AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will pour out my wrath on Pelusium,the stronghold of Egypt,and wipe out the hordes of Thebes.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will set fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21221AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21221AE\"></sup> to Egypt;Pelusium will writhe in agony.Thebes will be taken by storm;Memphis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21221AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21221AF\"></sup> will be in constant distress.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The young men of Heliopolis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21222AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21222AG\"></sup> and Bubastiswill fall by the sword,and the cities themselves will go into captivity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Dark will be the day at Tahpanhes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21223AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21223AH\"></sup>when I break the yoke of Egypt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21223AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21223AI\"></sup>there her proud strength will come to an end.She will be covered with clouds,and her villages will go into captivity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21223AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21223AJ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So I will inflict punishment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21224AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21224AK\"></sup> on Egypt,and they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In the eleventh year, in the first month on the seventh day, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21225AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21225AL\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Son of man, I have broken the arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21226AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21226AM\"></sup> of Pharaoh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21226AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21226AN\"></sup> king of Egypt. It has not been bound up to be healed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21226AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21226AO\"></sup> or put in a splint so that it may become strong enough to hold a sword.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against Pharaoh king of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21227AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21227AP\"></sup> I will break both his arms, the good arm as well as the broken one, and make the sword fall from his hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21227AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21227AQ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will disperse the Egyptians among the nations and scatter them through the countries.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21228AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21228AR\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I will strengthen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21229AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21229AS\"></sup> the arms of the king of Babylon and put my sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21229AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21229AT\"></sup> in his hand, but I will break the arms of Pharaoh, and he will groan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21229AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21229AU\"></sup> before him like a mortally wounded man.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will strengthen the arms of the king of Babylon, but the arms of Pharaoh will fall limp. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I put my sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21230AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21230AV\"></sup> into the hand of the king of Babylon and he brandishes it against Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21230AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21230AW\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will disperse the Egyptians among the nations and scatter them through the countries. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21231AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21231AX\"></sup>”"
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>In the eleventh year,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21232A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21232A\"></sup> in the third month on the first day, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21232B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21232B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, say to Pharaoh king of Egypt and to his hordes:“‘Who can be compared with you in majesty?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Consider Assyria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21234C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21234C\"></sup> once a cedar in Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21234D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21234D\"></sup>with beautiful branches overshadowing the forest;it towered on high,its top above the thick foliage.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21234E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21234E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21235F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21235F\"></sup> nourished it,deep springs made it grow tall;their streams flowedall around its baseand sent their channelsto all the trees of the field.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21235G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21235G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So it towered higher<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21236H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21236H\"></sup>than all the trees of the field;its boughs increasedand its branches grew long,spreading because of abundant waters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21236I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21236I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>All the birds of the skynested in its boughs,all the animals of the wildgave birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21237J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21237J\"></sup> under its branches;all the great nationslived in its shade.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21237K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21237K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It was majestic in beauty,with its spreading boughs,for its roots went downto abundant waters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21238L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21238L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The cedars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21239M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21239M\"></sup> in the garden of Godcould not rival it,nor could the junipersequal its boughs,nor could the plane trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21239N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21239N\"></sup>compare with its branches—no tree in the garden of Godcould match its beauty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21239O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21239O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I made it beautifulwith abundant branches,the envy of all the trees of Eden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21240P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21240P\"></sup>in the garden of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21240Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21240Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Because the great cedar towered over the thick foliage, and because it was proud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21241R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21241R\"></sup> of its height,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I gave it into the hands of the ruler of the nations, for him to deal with according to its wickedness. I cast it aside,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21242S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21242S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and the most ruthless of foreign nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21243T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21243T\"></sup> cut it down and left it. Its boughs fell on the mountains and in all the valleys;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21243U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21243U\"></sup> its branches lay broken in all the ravines of the land. All the nations of the earth came out from under its shade and left it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21243V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21243V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>All the birds settled on the fallen tree, and all the wild animals lived among its branches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21244W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21244W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore no other trees by the waters are ever to tower proudly on high, lifting their tops above the thick foliage. No other trees so well-watered are ever to reach such a height; they are all destined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21245X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21245X\"></sup> for death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21245Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21245Y\"></sup> for the earth below, among mortals who go down to the realm of the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21245Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21245Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: On the day it was brought down to the realm of the dead I covered the deep springs with mourning for it; I held back its streams, and its abundant waters were restrained. Because of it I clothed Lebanon with gloom, and all the trees of the field withered away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21246AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21246AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I made the nations tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21247AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21247AB\"></sup> at the sound of its fall when I brought it down to the realm of the dead to be with those who go down to the pit. Then all the trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21247AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21247AC\"></sup> of Eden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21247AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21247AD\"></sup> the choicest and best of Lebanon, the well-watered trees, were consoled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21247AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21247AE\"></sup> in the earth below.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21247AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21247AF\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They too, like the great cedar, had gone down to the realm of the dead, to those killed by the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21248AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21248AG\"></sup> along with the armed men who lived in its shade among the nations.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“‘Which of the trees of Eden can be compared with you in splendor and majesty? Yet you, too, will be brought down with the trees of Eden to the earth below; you will lie among the uncircumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21249AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21249AH\"></sup> with those killed by the sword.“‘This is Pharaoh and all his hordes, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>In the twelfth year, in the twelfth month on the first day, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21250A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21250A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, take up a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21251B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21251B\"></sup> concerning Pharaoh king of Egypt and say to him:“‘You are like a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21251C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21251C\"></sup> among the nations;you are like a monster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21251D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21251D\"></sup> in the seas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21251E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21251E\"></sup>thrashing about in your streams,churning the water with your feetand muddying the streams.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21251F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21251F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘With a great throng of peopleI will cast my net over you,and they will haul you up in my net.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21252G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21252G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will throw you on the landand hurl you on the open field.I will let all the birds of the sky settle on youand all the animals of the wild gorge themselves on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21253H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21253H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will spread your flesh on the mountainsand fill the valleys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21254I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21254I\"></sup> with your remains.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will drench the land with your flowing blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21255J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21255J\"></sup>all the way to the mountains,and the ravines will be filled with your flesh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21255K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21255K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When I snuff you out, I will cover the heavensand darken their stars;I will cover the sun with a cloud,and the moon will not give its light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21256L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21256L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All the shining lights in the heavensI will darken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21257M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21257M\"></sup> over you;I will bring darkness over your land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21257N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21257N\"></sup>declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will trouble the hearts of many peopleswhen I bring about your destruction among the nations,among lands you have not known.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will cause many peoples to be appalled at you,and their kings will shudder with horror because of youwhen I brandish my sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21259O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21259O\"></sup> before them.On the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21259P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21259P\"></sup> of your downfalleach of them will trembleevery moment for his life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21259Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21259Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“‘For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘The sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21260R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21260R\"></sup> of the king of Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21260S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21260S\"></sup>will come against you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21260T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21260T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will cause your hordes to fallby the swords of mighty men—the most ruthless of all nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21261U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21261U\"></sup>They will shatter the pride of Egypt,and all her hordes will be overthrown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21261V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21261V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will destroy all her cattlefrom beside abundant watersno longer to be stirred by the foot of manor muddied by the hooves of cattle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21262W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21262W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I will let her waters settleand make her streams flow like oil,declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When I make Egypt desolateand strip the land of everything in it,when I strike down all who live there,then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21264X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21264X\"></sup>’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“This is the lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21265Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21265Y\"></sup> they will chant for her. The daughters of the nations will chant it; for Egypt and all her hordes they will chant it, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the twelfth year, on the fifteenth day of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21266Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21266Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, wail for the hordes of Egypt and consign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21267AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21267AA\"></sup> to the earth below both her and the daughters of mighty nations, along with those who go down to the pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21267AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21267AB\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Say to them, ‘Are you more favored than others? Go down and be laid among the uncircumcised.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21268AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21268AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They will fall among those killed by the sword. The sword is drawn; let her be dragged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21269AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21269AD\"></sup> off with all her hordes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21269AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21269AE\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>From within the realm of the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21270AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21270AF\"></sup> the mighty leaders will say of Egypt and her allies, ‘They have come down and they lie with the uncircumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21270AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21270AG\"></sup> with those killed by the sword.’",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Assyria is there with her whole army; she is surrounded by the graves of all her slain, all who have fallen by the sword.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Their graves are in the depths of the pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21272AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21272AH\"></sup> and her army lies around her grave.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21272AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21272AI\"></sup> All who had spread terror in the land of the living are slain, fallen by the sword.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Elam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21273AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21273AJ\"></sup> is there, with all her hordes around her grave. All of them are slain, fallen by the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21273AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21273AK\"></sup> All who had spread terror in the land of the living<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21273AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21273AL\"></sup> went down uncircumcised to the earth below. They bear their shame with those who go down to the pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21273AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21273AM\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A bed is made for her among the slain, with all her hordes around her grave. All of them are uncircumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21274AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21274AN\"></sup> killed by the sword. Because their terror had spread in the land of the living, they bear their shame with those who go down to the pit; they are laid among the slain.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Meshek and Tubal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21275AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21275AO\"></sup> are there, with all their hordes around their graves. All of them are uncircumcised, killed by the sword because they spread their terror in the land of the living.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But they do not lie with the fallen warriors of old,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21276AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21276AP\"></sup> who went down to the realm of the dead with their weapons of war—their swords placed under their heads and their shields resting on their bones—though these warriors also had terrorized the land of the living.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“You too, Pharaoh, will be broken and will lie among the uncircumcised, with those killed by the sword.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21278AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21278AQ\"></sup> is there, her kings and all her princes; despite their power, they are laid with those killed by the sword. They lie with the uncircumcised, with those who go down to the pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21278AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21278AR\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“All the princes of the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21279AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21279AS\"></sup> and all the Sidonians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21279AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21279AT\"></sup> are there; they went down with the slain in disgrace despite the terror caused by their power. They lie uncircumcised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21279AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21279AU\"></sup> with those killed by the sword and bear their shame with those who go down to the pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21279AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21279AV\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Pharaoh—he and all his army—will see them and he will be consoled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21280AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21280AW\"></sup> for all his hordes that were killed by the sword, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Although I had him spread terror in the land of the living, Pharaoh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21281AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21281AX\"></sup> and all his hordes will be laid among the uncircumcised, with those killed by the sword, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21281AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21281AY\"></sup>"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, speak to your people and say to them: ‘When I bring the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21283A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21283A\"></sup> against a land, and the people of the land choose one of their men and make him their watchman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21283B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21283B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and he sees the sword coming against the land and blows the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21284C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21284C\"></sup> to warn the people,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>then if anyone hears the trumpet but does not heed the warning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21285D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21285D\"></sup> and the sword comes and takes their life, their blood will be on their own head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21285E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21285E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Since they heard the sound of the trumpet but did not heed the warning, their blood will be on their own head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21286F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21286F\"></sup> If they had heeded the warning, they would have saved themselves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21286G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21286G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But if the watchman sees the sword coming and does not blow the trumpet to warn the people and the sword comes and takes someone’s life, that person’s life will be taken because of their sin, but I will hold the watchman accountable for their blood.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21287H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21287H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Son of man, I have made you a watchman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21288I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21288I\"></sup> for the people of Israel; so hear the word I speak and give them warning from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21288J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21288J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When I say to the wicked, ‘You wicked person, you will surely die,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21289K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21289K\"></sup>’ and you do not speak out to dissuade them from their ways, that wicked person will die for their sin, and I will hold you accountable for their blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21289L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21289L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But if you do warn the wicked person to turn from their ways and they do not do so,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21290M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21290M\"></sup> they will die for their sin, though you yourself will be saved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21290N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21290N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Son of man, say to the Israelites, ‘This is what you are saying: “Our offenses and sins weigh us down, and we are wasting away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21291O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21291O\"></sup> because of them. How then can we live?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21291P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21291P\"></sup>”’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Say to them, ‘As surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I take no pleasure in the death of the wicked, but rather that they turn from their ways and live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21292Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21292Q\"></sup> Turn!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21292R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21292R\"></sup> Turn from your evil ways! Why will you die, people of Israel?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21292S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21292S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Therefore, son of man, say to your people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21293T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21293T\"></sup> ‘If someone who is righteous disobeys, that person’s former righteousness will count for nothing. And if someone who is wicked repents, that person’s former wickedness will not bring condemnation. The righteous person who sins will not be allowed to live even though they were formerly righteous.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21293U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21293U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If I tell a righteous person that they will surely live, but then they trust in their righteousness and do evil, none of the righteous things that person has done will be remembered; they will die for the evil they have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21294V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21294V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And if I say to a wicked person, ‘You will surely die,’ but they then turn away from their sin and do what is just<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21295W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21295W\"></sup> and right—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>if they give back what they took in pledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21296X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21296X\"></sup> for a loan, return what they have stolen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21296Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21296Y\"></sup> follow the decrees that give life, and do no evil—that person will surely live; they will not die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21296Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21296Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>None of the sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21297AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21297AA\"></sup> that person has committed will be remembered against them. They have done what is just and right; they will surely live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21297AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21297AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Yet your people say, ‘The way of the Lord is not just.’ But it is their way that is not just.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If a righteous person turns from their righteousness and does evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21299AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21299AC\"></sup> they will die for it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21299AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21299AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And if a wicked person turns away from their wickedness and does what is just and right, they will live by doing so.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21300AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21300AE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Yet you Israelites say, ‘The way of the Lord is not just.’ But I will judge each of you according to your own ways.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21301AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21301AF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In the twelfth year of our exile, in the tenth month on the fifth day, a man who had escaped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21302AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21302AG\"></sup> from Jerusalem came to me and said, “The city has fallen!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21302AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21302AH\"></sup>”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now the evening before the man arrived, the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was on me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21303AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21303AI\"></sup> and he opened my mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21303AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21303AJ\"></sup> before the man came to me in the morning. So my mouth was opened and I was no longer silent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21303AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21303AK\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Son of man, the people living in those ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21305AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21305AL\"></sup> in the land of Israel are saying, ‘Abraham was only one man, yet he possessed the land. But we are many;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21305AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21305AM\"></sup> surely the land has been given to us as our possession.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21305AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21305AN\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Since you eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21306AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21306AO\"></sup> meat with the blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21306AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21306AP\"></sup> still in it and look to your idols and shed blood, should you then possess the land?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21306AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21306AQ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You rely on your sword, you do detestable things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21307AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21307AR\"></sup> and each of you defiles his neighbor’s wife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21307AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21307AS\"></sup> Should you then possess the land?’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Say this to them: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: As surely as I live, those who are left in the ruins will fall by the sword, those out in the country I will give to the wild animals to be devoured, and those in strongholds and caves will die of a plague.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21308AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21308AT\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I will make the land a desolate waste, and her proud strength will come to an end, and the mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21309AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21309AU\"></sup> of Israel will become desolate so that no one will cross them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21309AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21309AV\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I have made the land a desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21310AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21310AW\"></sup> waste because of all the detestable things they have done.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21310AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21310AX\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“As for you, son of man, your people are talking together about you by the walls and at the doors of the houses, saying to each other, ‘Come and hear the message that has come from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>My people come to you, as they usually do, and sit before<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21312AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21312AY\"></sup> you to hear your words, but they do not put them into practice. Their mouths speak of love, but their hearts are greedy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21312AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21312AZ\"></sup> for unjust gain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21312BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21312BA\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Indeed, to them you are nothing more than one who sings love songs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21313BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21313BB\"></sup> with a beautiful voice and plays an instrument well, for they hear your words but do not put them into practice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21313BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21313BC\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“When all this comes true—and it surely will—then they will know that a prophet has been among them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21314BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21314BD\"></sup>”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy against the shepherds of Israel; prophesy and say to them: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Woe to you shepherds of Israel who only take care of yourselves! Should not shepherds take care of the flock?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21316A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21316A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You eat the curds, clothe yourselves with the wool and slaughter the choice animals, but you do not take care of the flock.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21317B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21317B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You have not strengthened the weak or healed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21318C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21318C\"></sup> the sick or bound up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21318D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21318D\"></sup> the injured. You have not brought back the strays or searched for the lost. You have ruled them harshly and brutally.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21318E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21318E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So they were scattered because there was no shepherd,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21319F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21319F\"></sup> and when they were scattered they became food for all the wild animals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21319G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21319G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>My sheep wandered over all the mountains and on every high hill.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21320H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21320H\"></sup> They were scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21320I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21320I\"></sup> over the whole earth, and no one searched or looked for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21320J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21320J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘Therefore, you shepherds, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>As surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, because my flock lacks a shepherd and so has been plundered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21322K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21322K\"></sup> and has become food for all the wild animals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21322L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21322L\"></sup> and because my shepherds did not search for my flock but cared for themselves rather than for my flock,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21322M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21322M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>therefore, you shepherds, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21324N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21324N\"></sup> the shepherds and will hold them accountable for my flock. I will remove them from tending the flock so that the shepherds can no longer feed themselves. I will rescue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21324O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21324O\"></sup> my flock from their mouths, and it will no longer be food for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21324P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21324P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“‘For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I myself will search for my sheep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21325Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21325Q\"></sup> and look after them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As a shepherd<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21326R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21326R\"></sup> looks after his scattered flock when he is with them, so will I look after my sheep. I will rescue them from all the places where they were scattered on a day of clouds and darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21326S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21326S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will bring them out from the nations and gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21327T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21327T\"></sup> them from the countries, and I will bring them into their own land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21327U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21327U\"></sup> I will pasture them on the mountains of Israel, in the ravines and in all the settlements in the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21327V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21327V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will tend them in a good pasture, and the mountain heights of Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21328W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21328W\"></sup> will be their grazing land. There they will lie down in good grazing land, and there they will feed in a rich pasture<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21328X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21328X\"></sup> on the mountains of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21328Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21328Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I myself will tend my sheep and have them lie down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21329Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21329Z\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21329AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21329AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will search for the lost and bring back the strays. I will bind up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21330AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21330AB\"></sup> the injured and strengthen the weak,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21330AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21330AC\"></sup> but the sleek and the strong I will destroy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21330AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21330AD\"></sup> I will shepherd the flock with justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21330AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21330AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“‘As for you, my flock, this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will judge between one sheep and another, and between rams and goats.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21331AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21331AF\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Is it not enough<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21332AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21332AG\"></sup> for you to feed on the good pasture? Must you also trample the rest of your pasture with your feet?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21332AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21332AH\"></sup> Is it not enough for you to drink clear water? Must you also muddy the rest with your feet?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Must my flock feed on what you have trampled and drink what you have muddied with your feet?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to them: See, I myself will judge between the fat sheep and the lean sheep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21334AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21334AI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Because you shove with flank and shoulder, butting all the weak sheep with your horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21335AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21335AJ\"></sup> until you have driven them away,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will save my flock, and they will no longer be plundered. I will judge between one sheep and another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21336AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21336AK\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will place over them one shepherd, my servant David, and he will tend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21337AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21337AL\"></sup> them; he will tend them and be their shepherd.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21337AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21337AM\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be their God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21338AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21338AN\"></sup> and my servant David<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21338AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21338AO\"></sup> will be prince among them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21338AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21338AP\"></sup> I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21338AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21338AQ\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“‘I will make a covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21339AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21339AR\"></sup> of peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21339AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21339AS\"></sup> with them and rid the land of savage beasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21339AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21339AT\"></sup> so that they may live in the wilderness and sleep in the forests in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21339AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21339AU\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will make them and the places surrounding my hill a blessing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21340AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21340AV\"></sup> I will send down showers in season;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21340AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21340AW\"></sup> there will be showers of blessing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21340AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21340AX\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The trees will yield their fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21341AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21341AY\"></sup> and the ground will yield its crops;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21341AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21341AZ\"></sup> the people will be secure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21341BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21341BA\"></sup> in their land. They will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I break the bars of their yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21341BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21341BB\"></sup> and rescue them from the hands of those who enslaved them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21341BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21341BC\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They will no longer be plundered by the nations, nor will wild animals devour them. They will live in safety,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21342BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21342BD\"></sup> and no one will make them afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21342BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21342BE\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I will provide for them a land renowned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21343BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21343BF\"></sup> for its crops, and they will no longer be victims of famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21343BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21343BG\"></sup> in the land or bear the scorn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21343BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21343BH\"></sup> of the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21343BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21343BI\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then they will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God, am with them and that they, the Israelites, are my people, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21344BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21344BJ\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>You are my sheep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21345BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21345BK\"></sup> the sheep of my pasture,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21345BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21345BL\"></sup> and I am your God, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against Mount Seir;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21347A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21347A\"></sup> prophesy against it",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against you, Mount Seir, and I will stretch out my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21348B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21348B\"></sup> against you and make you a desolate waste.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21348C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21348C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will turn your towns into ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21349D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21349D\"></sup> and you will be desolate. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21349E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21349E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“‘Because you harbored an ancient hostility and delivered the Israelites over to the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21350F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21350F\"></sup> at the time of their calamity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21350G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21350G\"></sup> the time their punishment reached its climax,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21350H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21350H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>therefore as surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I will give you over to bloodshed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21351I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21351I\"></sup> and it will pursue you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21351J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21351J\"></sup> Since you did not hate bloodshed, bloodshed will pursue you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will make Mount Seir a desolate waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21352K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21352K\"></sup> and cut off from it all who come and go.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21352L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21352L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will fill your mountains with the slain; those killed by the sword will fall on your hills and in your valleys and in all your ravines.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21353M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21353M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make you desolate forever;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21354N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21354N\"></sup> your towns will not be inhabited. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21354O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21354O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘Because you have said, “These two nations and countries will be ours and we will take possession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21355P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21355P\"></sup> of them,” even though I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was there,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>therefore as surely as I live, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I will treat you in accordance with the anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21356Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21356Q\"></sup> and jealousy you showed in your hatred of them and I will make myself known among them when I judge you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21356R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21356R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then you will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have heard all the contemptible things you have said against the mountains of Israel. You said, “They have been laid waste and have been given over to us to devour.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21357S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21357S\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You boasted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21358T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21358T\"></sup> against me and spoke against me without restraint, and I heard it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21358U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21358U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: While the whole earth rejoices, I will make you desolate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21359V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21359V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Because you rejoiced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21360W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21360W\"></sup> when the inheritance of Israel became desolate, that is how I will treat you. You will be desolate, Mount Seir,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21360X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21360X\"></sup> you and all of Edom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21360Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21360Y\"></sup> Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>“Son of man, prophesy to the mountains of Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21361A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21361A\"></sup> and say, ‘Mountains of Israel, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21362B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21362B\"></sup> The enemy said of you, “Aha!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21362C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21362C\"></sup> The ancient heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21362D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21362D\"></sup> have become our possession.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21362E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21362E\"></sup>”’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore prophesy and say, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Because they ravaged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21363F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21363F\"></sup> and crushed you from every side so that you became the possession of the rest of the nations and the object of people’s malicious talk and slander,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21363G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21363G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>therefore, mountains of Israel, hear the word of the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to the mountains and hills, to the ravines and valleys,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21364H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21364H\"></sup> to the desolate ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21364I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21364I\"></sup> and the deserted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21364J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21364J\"></sup> towns that have been plundered and ridiculed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21364K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21364K\"></sup> by the rest of the nations around you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21364L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21364L\"></sup>—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: In my burning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21365M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21365M\"></sup> zeal I have spoken against the rest of the nations, and against all Edom, for with glee and with malice in their hearts they made my land their own possession so that they might plunder its pastureland.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21365N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21365N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore prophesy concerning the land of Israel and say to the mountains and hills, to the ravines and valleys: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I speak in my jealous wrath because you have suffered the scorn of the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21366O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21366O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I swear with uplifted hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21367P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21367P\"></sup> that the nations around you will also suffer scorn.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21367Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21367Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘But you, mountains of Israel, will produce branches and fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21368R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21368R\"></sup> for my people Israel, for they will soon come home.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I am concerned for you and will look on you with favor; you will be plowed and sown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21369S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21369S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and I will cause many people to live on you—yes, all of Israel. The towns will be inhabited and the ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21370T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21370T\"></sup> rebuilt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21370U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21370U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will increase the number of people and animals living on you, and they will be fruitful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21371V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21371V\"></sup> and become numerous. I will settle people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21371W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21371W\"></sup> on you as in the past<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21371X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21371X\"></sup> and will make you prosper more than before.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21371Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21371Y\"></sup> Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will cause people, my people Israel, to live on you. They will possess you, and you will be their inheritance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21372Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21372Z\"></sup> you will never again deprive them of their children.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Because some say to you, “You devour people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21373AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21373AA\"></sup> and deprive your nation of its children,”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>therefore you will no longer devour people or make your nation childless, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>No longer will I make you hear the taunts of the nations, and no longer will you suffer the scorn of the peoples or cause your nation to fall, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21375AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21375AB\"></sup>’”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Again the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Son of man, when the people of Israel were living in their own land, they defiled it by their conduct and their actions. Their conduct was like a woman’s monthly uncleanness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21377AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21377AC\"></sup> in my sight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21377AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21377AD\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So I poured out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21378AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21378AE\"></sup> my wrath on them because they had shed blood in the land and because they had defiled it with their idols.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I dispersed them among the nations, and they were scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21379AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21379AF\"></sup> through the countries; I judged them according to their conduct and their actions.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21379AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21379AG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And wherever they went among the nations they profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21380AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21380AH\"></sup> my holy name, for it was said of them, ‘These are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s people, and yet they had to leave his land.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21380AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21380AI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I had concern for my holy name, which the people of Israel profaned among the nations where they had gone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21381AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21381AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Therefore say to the Israelites, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: It is not for your sake, people of Israel, that I am going to do these things, but for the sake of my holy name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21382AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21382AK\"></sup> which you have profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21382AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21382AL\"></sup> among the nations where you have gone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21382AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21382AM\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will show the holiness of my great name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21383AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21383AN\"></sup> which has been profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21383AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21383AO\"></sup> among the nations, the name you have profaned among them. Then the nations will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21383AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21383AP\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I am proved holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21383AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21383AQ\"></sup> through you before their eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21383AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21383AR\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“‘For I will take you out of the nations; I will gather you from all the countries and bring you back into your own land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21384AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21384AS\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will sprinkle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21385AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21385AT\"></sup> clean water on you, and you will be clean; I will cleanse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21385AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21385AU\"></sup> you from all your impurities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21385AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21385AV\"></sup> and from all your idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21385AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21385AW\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will give you a new heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21386AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21386AX\"></sup> and put a new spirit in you; I will remove from you your heart of stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21386AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21386AY\"></sup> and give you a heart of flesh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21386AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21386AZ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And I will put my Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21387BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21387BA\"></sup> in you and move you to follow my decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21387BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21387BB\"></sup> and be careful to keep my laws.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21387BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21387BC\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then you will live in the land I gave your ancestors; you will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21388BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21388BD\"></sup> and I will be your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21388BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21388BE\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I will save you from all your uncleanness. I will call for the grain and make it plentiful and will not bring famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21389BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21389BF\"></sup> upon you.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I will increase the fruit of the trees and the crops of the field, so that you will no longer suffer disgrace among the nations because of famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21390BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21390BG\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Then you will remember your evil ways and wicked deeds, and you will loathe yourselves for your sins and detestable practices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21391BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21391BH\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>I want you to know that I am not doing this for your sake, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21392BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21392BI\"></sup> and disgraced for your conduct, people of Israel!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21392BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21392BJ\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: On the day I cleanse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21393BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21393BK\"></sup> you from all your sins, I will resettle your towns, and the ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21393BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21393BL\"></sup> will be rebuilt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21393BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21393BM\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>The desolate land will be cultivated instead of lying desolate in the sight of all who pass through it.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>They will say, “This land that was laid waste has become like the garden of Eden;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21395BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21395BN\"></sup> the cities that were lying in ruins, desolate and destroyed, are now fortified and inhabited.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21395BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21395BO\"></sup>”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then the nations around you that remain will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have rebuilt what was destroyed and have replanted what was desolate. I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken, and I will do it.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21396BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21396BP\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Once again I will yield to Israel’s plea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21397BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21397BQ\"></sup> and do this for them: I will make their people as numerous as sheep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21397BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21397BR\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>as numerous as the flocks for offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21398BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21398BS\"></sup> at Jerusalem during her appointed festivals. So will the ruined cities be filled with flocks of people. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21398BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21398BT\"></sup>”"
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>The hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was on me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21399A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21399A\"></sup> and he brought me out by the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21399B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21399B\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and set me in the middle of a valley;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21399C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21399C\"></sup> it was full of bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21399D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21399D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He led me back and forth among them, and I saw a great many bones on the floor of the valley, bones that were very dry.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He asked me, “Son of man, can these bones live?”I said, “Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you alone know.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21401E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21401E\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then he said to me, “Prophesy to these bones and say to them, ‘Dry bones, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21402F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21402F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to these bones: I will make breath enter you, and you will come to life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21403G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21403G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will attach tendons to you and make flesh come upon you and cover you with skin; I will put breath in you, and you will come to life. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21404H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21404H\"></sup>’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I prophesied as I was commanded. And as I was prophesying, there was a noise, a rattling sound, and the bones came together, bone to bone.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I looked, and tendons and flesh appeared on them and skin covered them, but there was no breath in them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then he said to me, “Prophesy to the breath;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21407I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21407I\"></sup> prophesy, son of man, and say to it, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Come, breath, from the four winds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21407J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21407J\"></sup> and breathe into these slain, that they may live.’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So I prophesied as he commanded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21408K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21408K\"></sup> me, and breath entered them; they came to life and stood up on their feet—a vast army.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21408L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21408L\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then he said to me: “Son of man, these bones are the people of Israel. They say, ‘Our bones are dried up and our hope is gone; we are cut off.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21409M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21409M\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore prophesy and say to them: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: My people, I am going to open your graves and bring you up from them; I will bring you back to the land of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21410N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21410N\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then you, my people, will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21411O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21411O\"></sup> when I open your graves and bring you up from them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21411P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21411P\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will put my Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21412Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21412Q\"></sup> in you and you will live, and I will settle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21412R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21412R\"></sup> you in your own land. Then you will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken, and I have done it, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21412S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21412S\"></sup>’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Son of man, take a stick of wood and write on it, ‘Belonging to Judah and the Israelites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21414T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21414T\"></sup> associated with him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21414U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21414U\"></sup>’ Then take another stick of wood, and write on it, ‘Belonging to Joseph (that is, to Ephraim) and all the Israelites associated with him.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Join them together into one stick so that they will become one in your hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21415V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21415V\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“When your people ask you, ‘Won’t you tell us what you mean by this?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21416W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21416W\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am going to take the stick of Joseph—which is in Ephraim’s hand—and of the Israelite tribes associated with him, and join it to Judah’s stick. I will make them into a single stick of wood, and they will become one in my hand.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21417X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21417X\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Hold before their eyes the sticks you have written on",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and say to them, ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will take the Israelites out of the nations where they have gone. I will gather them from all around and bring them back into their own land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21419Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21419Y\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will make them one nation in the land, on the mountains of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21420Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21420Z\"></sup> There will be one king over all of them and they will never again be two nations or be divided into two kingdoms.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21420AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21420AA\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They will no longer defile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21421AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21421AB\"></sup> themselves with their idols and vile images or with any of their offenses, for I will save them from all their sinful backsliding,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21421AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21421AC\"></sup> and I will cleanse them. They will be my people, and I will be their God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21421AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21421AD\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“‘My servant David<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21422AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21422AE\"></sup> will be king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21422AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21422AF\"></sup> over them, and they will all have one shepherd.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21422AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21422AG\"></sup> They will follow my laws and be careful to keep my decrees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21422AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21422AH\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They will live in the land I gave to my servant Jacob, the land where your ancestors lived.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21423AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21423AI\"></sup> They and their children and their children’s children will live there forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21423AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21423AJ\"></sup> and David my servant will be their prince forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21423AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21423AK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will make a covenant of peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21424AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21424AL\"></sup> with them; it will be an everlasting covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21424AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21424AM\"></sup> I will establish them and increase their numbers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21424AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21424AN\"></sup> and I will put my sanctuary among them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21424AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21424AO\"></sup> forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21424AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21424AP\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>My dwelling place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21425AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21425AQ\"></sup> will be with them; I will be their God, and they will be my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21425AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21425AR\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then the nations will know that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> make Israel holy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21426AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21426AS\"></sup> when my sanctuary is among them forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21426AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21426AT\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against Gog,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21428A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21428A\"></sup> of the land of Magog,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21428B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21428B\"></sup> the chief prince of Meshek and Tubal;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21428C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21428C\"></sup> prophesy against him",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against you, Gog, chief prince of Meshek and Tubal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21429D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21429D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will turn you around, put hooks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21430E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21430E\"></sup> in your jaws and bring you out with your whole army—your horses, your horsemen fully armed, and a great horde with large and small shields, all of them brandishing their swords.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21430F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21430F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Persia, Cush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21431G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21431G\"></sup> and Put<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21431H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21431H\"></sup> will be with them, all with shields and helmets,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>also Gomer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21432I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21432I\"></sup> with all its troops, and Beth Togarmah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21432J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21432J\"></sup> from the far north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21432K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21432K\"></sup> with all its troops—the many nations with you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘Get ready; be prepared,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21433L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21433L\"></sup> you and all the hordes gathered about you, and take command of them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>After many days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21434M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21434M\"></sup> you will be called to arms. In future years you will invade a land that has recovered from war, whose people were gathered from many nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21434N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21434N\"></sup> to the mountains of Israel, which had long been desolate. They had been brought out from the nations, and now all of them live in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21434O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21434O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You and all your troops and the many nations with you will go up, advancing like a storm;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21435P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21435P\"></sup> you will be like a cloud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21435Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21435Q\"></sup> covering the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21435R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21435R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: On that day thoughts will come into your mind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21436S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21436S\"></sup> and you will devise an evil scheme.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21436T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21436T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You will say, “I will invade a land of unwalled villages; I will attack a peaceful and unsuspecting people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21437U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21437U\"></sup>—all of them living without walls and without gates and bars.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21437V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21437V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will plunder and loot and turn my hand against the resettled ruins and the people gathered from the nations, rich in livestock and goods, living at the center of the land.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Sheba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21439W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21439W\"></sup> and Dedan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21439X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21439X\"></sup> and the merchants of Tarshish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21439Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21439Y\"></sup> and all her villages will say to you, “Have you come to plunder? Have you gathered your hordes to loot, to carry off silver and gold, to take away livestock and goods and to seize much plunder?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21439Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21439Z\"></sup>”’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Therefore, son of man, prophesy and say to Gog: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: In that day, when my people Israel are living in safety,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21440AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21440AA\"></sup> will you not take notice of it?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You will come from your place in the far north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21441AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21441AB\"></sup> you and many nations with you, all of them riding on horses, a great horde, a mighty army.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21441AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21441AC\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will advance against my people Israel like a cloud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21442AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21442AD\"></sup> that covers the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21442AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21442AE\"></sup> In days to come, Gog, I will bring you against my land, so that the nations may know me when I am proved holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21442AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21442AF\"></sup> through you before their eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21442AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21442AG\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You are the one I spoke of in former days by my servants the prophets of Israel. At that time they prophesied for years that I would bring you against them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This is what will happen in that day: When Gog attacks the land of Israel, my hot anger will be aroused, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>In my zeal and fiery wrath I declare that at that time there shall be a great earthquake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21445AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21445AH\"></sup> in the land of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21445AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21445AI\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The fish in the sea, the birds in the sky, the beasts of the field, every creature that moves along the ground, and all the people on the face of the earth will tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21446AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21446AJ\"></sup> at my presence. The mountains will be overturned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21446AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21446AK\"></sup> the cliffs will crumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21446AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21446AL\"></sup> and every wall will fall to the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21446AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21446AM\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will summon a sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21447AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21447AN\"></sup> against Gog on all my mountains, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Every man’s sword will be against his brother.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21447AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21447AO\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will execute judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21448AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21448AP\"></sup> on him with plague and bloodshed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21448AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21448AQ\"></sup> I will pour down torrents of rain, hailstones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21448AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21448AR\"></sup> and burning sulfur<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21448AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21448AS\"></sup> on him and on his troops and on the many nations with him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21448AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21448AT\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And so I will show my greatness and my holiness, and I will make myself known in the sight of many nations. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21449AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21449AU\"></sup>’"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span>“Son of man, prophesy against Gog<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21450A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21450A\"></sup> and say: ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am against you, Gog, chief prince of Meshek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21450B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21450B\"></sup> and Tubal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21450C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21450C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will turn you around and drag you along. I will bring you from the far north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21451D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21451D\"></sup> and send you against the mountains of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21451E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21451E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then I will strike your bow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21452F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21452F\"></sup> from your left hand and make your arrows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21452G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21452G\"></sup> drop from your right hand.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>On the mountains of Israel you will fall, you and all your troops and the nations with you. I will give you as food to all kinds of carrion birds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21453H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21453H\"></sup> and to the wild animals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21453I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21453I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You will fall in the open field, for I have spoken, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21454J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21454J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will send fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21455K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21455K\"></sup> on Magog<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21455L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21455L\"></sup> and on those who live in safety in the coastlands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21455M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21455M\"></sup> and they will know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21455N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21455N\"></sup> that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘I will make known my holy name among my people Israel. I will no longer let my holy name be profaned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21456O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21456O\"></sup> and the nations will know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21456P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21456P\"></sup> that I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> am the Holy One in Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21456Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21456Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It is coming! It will surely take place, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. This is the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21457R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21457R\"></sup> I have spoken of.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘Then those who live in the towns of Israel will go out and use the weapons for fuel and burn them up—the small and large shields, the bows and arrows,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21458S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21458S\"></sup> the war clubs and spears. For seven years they will use them for fuel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21458T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21458T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will not need to gather wood from the fields or cut it from the forests, because they will use the weapons for fuel. And they will plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21459U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21459U\"></sup> those who plundered them and loot those who looted them, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21459V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21459V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“‘On that day I will give Gog a burial place in Israel, in the valley of those who travel east of the Sea. It will block the way of travelers, because Gog and all his hordes will be buried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21460W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21460W\"></sup> there. So it will be called the Valley of Hamon Gog.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21460X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21460X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“‘For seven months the Israelites will be burying them in order to cleanse the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21461Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21461Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>All the people of the land will bury them, and the day I display my glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21462Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21462Z\"></sup> will be a memorable day for them, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>People will be continually employed in cleansing the land. They will spread out across the land and, along with others, they will bury any bodies that are lying on the ground.“‘After the seven months they will carry out a more detailed search.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As they go through the land, anyone who sees a human bone will leave a marker beside it until the gravediggers bury it in the Valley of Hamon Gog,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>near a town called Hamonah. And so they will cleanse the land.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Son of man, this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Call out to every kind of bird<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21466AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21466AA\"></sup> and all the wild animals: ‘Assemble and come together from all around to the sacrifice I am preparing for you, the great sacrifice on the mountains of Israel. There you will eat flesh and drink blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21466AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21466AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You will eat the flesh of mighty men and drink the blood of the princes of the earth as if they were rams and lambs, goats and bulls—all of them fattened animals from Bashan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21467AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21467AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>At the sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21468AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21468AD\"></sup> I am preparing for you, you will eat fat till you are glutted and drink blood till you are drunk.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>At my table you will eat your fill of horses and riders, mighty men and soldiers of every kind,’ declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21469AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21469AE\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“I will display my glory among the nations, and all the nations will see the punishment I inflict and the hand I lay on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21470AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21470AF\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>From that day forward the people of Israel will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And the nations will know that the people of Israel went into exile for their sin, because they were unfaithful to me. So I hid my face from them and handed them over to their enemies, and they all fell by the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21472AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21472AG\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I dealt with them according to their uncleanness and their offenses, and I hid my face from them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21473AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21473AH\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will now restore the fortunes of Jacob<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21474AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21474AI\"></sup> and will have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21474AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21474AJ\"></sup> on all the people of Israel, and I will be zealous for my holy name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21474AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21474AK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will forget their shame and all the unfaithfulness they showed toward me when they lived in safety<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21475AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21475AL\"></sup> in their land with no one to make them afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21475AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21475AM\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When I have brought them back from the nations and have gathered them from the countries of their enemies, I will be proved holy through them in the sight of many nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21476AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21476AN\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God, for though I sent them into exile among the nations, I will gather them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21477AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21477AO\"></sup> to their own land, not leaving any behind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21477AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21477AP\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I will no longer hide my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21478AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21478AQ\"></sup> from them, for I will pour out my Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21478AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21478AR\"></sup> on the people of Israel, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21478AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21478AS\"></sup>”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>In the twenty-fifth year of our exile, at the beginning of the year, on the tenth of the month, in the fourteenth year after the fall of the city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21479A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21479A\"></sup>—on that very day the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was on me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21479B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21479B\"></sup> and he took me there.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In visions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21480C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21480C\"></sup> of God he took me to the land of Israel and set me on a very high mountain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21480D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21480D\"></sup> on whose south side were some buildings that looked like a city.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He took me there, and I saw a man whose appearance was like bronze;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21481E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21481E\"></sup> he was standing in the gateway with a linen cord and a measuring rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21481F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21481F\"></sup> in his hand.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The man said to me, “Son of man, look carefully and listen closely and pay attention to everything I am going to show you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21482G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21482G\"></sup> for that is why you have been brought here. Tell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21482H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21482H\"></sup> the people of Israel everything you see.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21482I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21482I\"></sup>”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I saw a wall completely surrounding the temple area. The length of the measuring rod in the man’s hand was six long cubits, each of which was a cubit and a handbreadth. He measured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21483J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21483J\"></sup> the wall; it was one measuring rod thick and one rod high.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then he went to the east gate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21484K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21484K\"></sup> He climbed its steps and measured the threshold of the gate; it was one rod deep.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The alcoves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21485L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21485L\"></sup> for the guards were one rod long and one rod wide, and the projecting walls between the alcoves were five cubits thick. And the threshold of the gate next to the portico facing the temple was one rod deep.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he measured the portico of the gateway;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>it was eight cubits deep and its jambs were two cubits thick. The portico of the gateway faced the temple.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Inside the east gate were three alcoves on each side; the three had the same measurements, and the faces of the projecting walls on each side had the same measurements.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then he measured the width of the entrance of the gateway; it was ten cubits and its length was thirteen cubits.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In front of each alcove was a wall one cubit high, and the alcoves were six cubits square.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he measured the gateway from the top of the rear wall of one alcove to the top of the opposite one; the distance was twenty-five cubits from one parapet opening to the opposite one.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He measured along the faces of the projecting walls all around the inside of the gateway—sixty cubits. The measurement was up to the portico facing the courtyard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21492M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21492M\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The distance from the entrance of the gateway to the far end of its portico was fifty cubits.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The alcoves and the projecting walls inside the gateway were surmounted by narrow parapet openings all around, as was the portico; the openings all around faced inward. The faces of the projecting walls were decorated with palm trees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21494N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21494N\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then he brought me into the outer court.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21495O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21495O\"></sup> There I saw some rooms and a pavement that had been constructed all around the court; there were thirty rooms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21495P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21495P\"></sup> along the pavement.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21495Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21495Q\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>It abutted the sides of the gateways and was as wide as they were long; this was the lower pavement.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then he measured the distance from the inside of the lower gateway to the outside of the inner court;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21497R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21497R\"></sup> it was a hundred cubits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21497S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21497S\"></sup> on the east side as well as on the north.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then he measured the length and width of the north gate, leading into the outer court.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Its alcoves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21499T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21499T\"></sup>—three on each side—its projecting walls and its portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21499U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21499U\"></sup> had the same measurements as those of the first gateway. It was fifty cubits long and twenty-five cubits wide.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Its openings, its portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21500V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21500V\"></sup> and its palm tree decorations had the same measurements as those of the gate facing east. Seven steps led up to it, with its portico opposite them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21500W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21500W\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>There was a gate to the inner court facing the north gate, just as there was on the east. He measured from one gate to the opposite one; it was a hundred cubits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21501X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21501X\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then he led me to the south side and I saw the south gate. He measured its jambs and its portico, and they had the same measurements<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21502Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21502Y\"></sup> as the others.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The gateway and its portico had narrow openings all around, like the openings of the others. It was fifty cubits long and twenty-five cubits wide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21503Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21503Z\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Seven steps led up to it, with its portico opposite them; it had palm tree decorations on the faces of the projecting walls on each side.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21504AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21504AA\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The inner court<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21505AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21505AB\"></sup> also had a gate facing south, and he measured from this gate to the outer gate on the south side; it was a hundred cubits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21505AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21505AC\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then he brought me into the inner court through the south gate, and he measured the south gate; it had the same measurements<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21506AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21506AD\"></sup> as the others.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Its alcoves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21507AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21507AE\"></sup> its projecting walls and its portico had the same measurements as the others. The gateway and its portico had openings all around. It was fifty cubits long and twenty-five cubits wide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21507AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21507AF\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>(The porticoes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21508AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21508AG\"></sup> of the gateways around the inner court were twenty-five cubits wide and five cubits deep.)",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Its portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21509AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21509AH\"></sup> faced the outer court; palm trees decorated its jambs, and eight steps led up to it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21509AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21509AI\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then he brought me to the inner court on the east side, and he measured the gateway; it had the same measurements<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21510AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21510AJ\"></sup> as the others.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Its alcoves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21511AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21511AK\"></sup> its projecting walls and its portico had the same measurements as the others. The gateway and its portico had openings all around. It was fifty cubits long and twenty-five cubits wide.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Its portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21512AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21512AL\"></sup> faced the outer court; palm trees decorated the jambs on either side, and eight steps led up to it.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then he brought me to the north gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21513AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21513AM\"></sup> and measured it. It had the same measurements<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21513AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21513AN\"></sup> as the others,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>as did its alcoves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21514AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21514AO\"></sup> its projecting walls and its portico, and it had openings all around. It was fifty cubits long and twenty-five cubits wide.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Its portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21515AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21515AP\"></sup> faced the outer court; palm trees decorated the jambs on either side, and eight steps led up to it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21515AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21515AQ\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>A room with a doorway was by the portico in each of the inner gateways, where the burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21516AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21516AR\"></sup> were washed.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>In the portico of the gateway were two tables on each side, on which the burnt offerings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21517AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21517AS\"></sup> sin offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21517AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21517AT\"></sup> and guilt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21517AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21517AU\"></sup> were slaughtered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21517AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21517AV\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>By the outside wall of the portico of the gateway, near the steps at the entrance of the north gateway were two tables, and on the other side of the steps were two tables.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So there were four tables on one side of the gateway and four on the other—eight tables in all—on which the sacrifices were slaughtered.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>There were also four tables of dressed stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21520AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21520AW\"></sup> for the burnt offerings, each a cubit and a half long, a cubit and a half wide and a cubit high. On them were placed the utensils for slaughtering the burnt offerings and the other sacrifices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21520AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21520AX\"></sup>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And double-pronged hooks, each a handbreadth long, were attached to the wall all around. The tables were for the flesh of the offerings.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Outside the inner gate, within the inner court, were two rooms, one at the side of the north gate and facing south, and another at the side of the south gate and facing north.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>He said to me, “The room facing south is for the priests who guard the temple,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21523AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21523AY\"></sup>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>and the room facing north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21524AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21524AZ\"></sup> is for the priests who guard the altar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21524BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21524BA\"></sup> These are the sons of Zadok,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21524BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21524BB\"></sup> who are the only Levites who may draw near to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to minister before him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21524BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21524BC\"></sup>”",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Then he measured the court: It was square—a hundred cubits long and a hundred cubits wide. And the altar was in front of the temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21525BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21525BD\"></sup>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>He brought me to the portico of the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21526BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21526BE\"></sup> and measured the jambs of the portico; they were five cubits wide on either side. The width of the entrance was fourteen cubits and its projecting walls were three cubits wide on either side.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>The portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21527BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21527BF\"></sup> was twenty cubits wide, and twelve cubits from front to back. It was reached by a flight of stairs, and there were pillars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21527BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21527BG\"></sup> on each side of the jambs."
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span>Then the man brought me to the main hall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21528A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21528A\"></sup> and measured the jambs; the width of the jambs was six cubits on each side.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The entrance was ten cubits wide, and the projecting walls on each side of it were five cubits wide. He also measured the main hall; it was forty cubits long and twenty cubits wide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21529B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21529B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then he went into the inner sanctuary and measured the jambs of the entrance; each was two cubits wide. The entrance was six cubits wide, and the projecting walls on each side of it were seven cubits wide.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And he measured the length of the inner sanctuary; it was twenty cubits, and its width was twenty cubits across the end of the main hall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21531C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21531C\"></sup> He said to me, “This is the Most Holy Place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21531D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21531D\"></sup>”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then he measured the wall of the temple; it was six cubits thick, and each side room around the temple was four cubits wide.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The side rooms were on three levels, one above another, thirty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21533E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21533E\"></sup> on each level. There were ledges all around the wall of the temple to serve as supports for the side rooms, so that the supports were not inserted into the wall of the temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21533F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21533F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The side rooms all around the temple were wider at each successive level. The structure surrounding the temple was built in ascending stages, so that the rooms widened as one went upward. A stairway<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21534G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21534G\"></sup> went up from the lowest floor to the top floor through the middle floor.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I saw that the temple had a raised base all around it, forming the foundation of the side rooms. It was the length of the rod, six long cubits.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The outer wall of the side rooms was five cubits thick. The open area between the side rooms of the temple",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and the priests’ rooms was twenty cubits wide all around the temple.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There were entrances to the side rooms from the open area, one on the north and another on the south; and the base adjoining the open area was five cubits wide all around.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The building facing the temple courtyard on the west side was seventy cubits wide. The wall of the building was five cubits thick all around, and its length was ninety cubits.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he measured the temple; it was a hundred cubits long, and the temple courtyard and the building with its walls were also a hundred cubits long.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The width of the temple courtyard on the east, including the front of the temple, was a hundred cubits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21541H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21541H\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then he measured the length of the building facing the courtyard at the rear of the temple, including its galleries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21542I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21542I\"></sup> on each side; it was a hundred cubits.The main hall, the inner sanctuary and the portico facing the court,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>as well as the thresholds and the narrow windows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21543J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21543J\"></sup> and galleries around the three of them—everything beyond and including the threshold was covered with wood. The floor, the wall up to the windows, and the windows were covered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21543K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21543K\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the space above the outside of the entrance to the inner sanctuary and on the walls at regular intervals all around the inner and outer sanctuary",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>were carved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21545L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21545L\"></sup> cherubim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21545M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21545M\"></sup> and palm trees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21545N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21545N\"></sup> Palm trees alternated with cherubim. Each cherub had two faces:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21545O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21545O\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the face of a human being toward the palm tree on one side and the face of a lion toward the palm tree on the other. They were carved all around the whole temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21546P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21546P\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>From the floor to the area above the entrance, cherubim and palm trees were carved on the wall of the main hall.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The main hall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21548Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21548Q\"></sup> had a rectangular doorframe, and the one at the front of the Most Holy Place was similar.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>There was a wooden altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21549R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21549R\"></sup> three cubits high and two cubits square; its corners, its base and its sides were of wood. The man said to me, “This is the table<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21549S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21549S\"></sup> that is before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Both the main hall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21550T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21550T\"></sup> and the Most Holy Place had double doors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21550U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21550U\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Each door had two leaves—two hinged leaves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21551V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21551V\"></sup> for each door.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And on the doors of the main hall were carved cherubim and palm trees like those carved on the walls, and there was a wooden overhang on the front of the portico.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>On the sidewalls of the portico were narrow windows with palm trees carved on each side. The side rooms of the temple also had overhangs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21553W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21553W\"></sup>"
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then the man led me northward into the outer court and brought me to the rooms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21554A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21554A\"></sup> opposite the temple courtyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21554B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21554B\"></sup> and opposite the outer wall on the north side.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21554C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21554C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The building whose door faced north was a hundred cubits long and fifty cubits wide.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Both in the section twenty cubits from the inner court and in the section opposite the pavement of the outer court, gallery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21556D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21556D\"></sup> faced gallery at the three levels.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21556E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21556E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In front of the rooms was an inner passageway ten cubits wide and a hundred cubits long. Their doors were on the north.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21557F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21557F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now the upper rooms were narrower, for the galleries took more space from them than from the rooms on the lower and middle floors of the building.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The rooms on the top floor had no pillars, as the courts had; so they were smaller in floor space than those on the lower and middle floors.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There was an outer wall parallel to the rooms and the outer court; it extended in front of the rooms for fifty cubits.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>While the row of rooms on the side next to the outer court was fifty cubits long, the row on the side nearest the sanctuary was a hundred cubits long.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The lower rooms had an entrance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21562G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21562G\"></sup> on the east side as one enters them from the outer court.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>On the south side along the length of the wall of the outer court, adjoining the temple courtyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21563H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21563H\"></sup> and opposite the outer wall, were rooms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21563I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21563I\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>with a passageway in front of them. These were like the rooms on the north; they had the same length and width, with similar exits and dimensions. Similar to the doorways on the north",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>were the doorways of the rooms on the south. There was a doorway at the beginning of the passageway that was parallel to the corresponding wall extending eastward, by which one enters the rooms.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he said to me, “The north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21566J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21566J\"></sup> and south rooms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21566K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21566K\"></sup> facing the temple courtyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21566L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21566L\"></sup> are the priests’ rooms, where the priests who approach the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will eat the most holy offerings. There they will put the most holy offerings—the grain offerings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21566M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21566M\"></sup> the sin offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21566N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21566N\"></sup> and the guilt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21566O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21566O\"></sup>—for the place is holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21566P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21566P\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Once the priests enter the holy precincts, they are not to go into the outer court until they leave behind the garments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21567Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21567Q\"></sup> in which they minister, for these are holy. They are to put on other clothes before they go near the places that are for the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21567R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21567R\"></sup>”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When he had finished measuring what was inside the temple area, he led me out by the east gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21568S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21568S\"></sup> and measured the area all around:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He measured the east side with the measuring rod; it was five hundred cubits.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He measured the north side; it was five hundred cubits by the measuring rod.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He measured the south side; it was five hundred cubits by the measuring rod.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then he turned to the west side and measured; it was five hundred cubits by the measuring rod.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So he measured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21573T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21573T\"></sup> the area<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21573U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21573U\"></sup> on all four sides. It had a wall around it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21573V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21573V\"></sup> five hundred cubits long and five hundred cubits wide,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21573W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21573W\"></sup> to separate the holy from the common.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21573X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21573X\"></sup>"
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>Then the man brought me to the gate facing east,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21574A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21574A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and I saw the glory of the God of Israel coming from the east. His voice was like the roar of rushing waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21575B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21575B\"></sup> and the land was radiant with his glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21575C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21575C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The vision I saw was like the vision I had seen when he came to destroy the city and like the visions I had seen by the Kebar River, and I fell facedown.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21577D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21577D\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> entered the temple through the gate facing east.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21577E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21577E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21578F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21578F\"></sup> lifted me up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21578G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21578G\"></sup> and brought me into the inner court, and the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21578H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21578H\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> filled the temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21578I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21578I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>While the man was standing beside me, I heard someone speaking to me from inside the temple.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He said: “Son of man, this is the place of my throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21580J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21580J\"></sup> and the place for the soles of my feet. This is where I will live among the Israelites forever. The people of Israel will never again defile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21580K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21580K\"></sup> my holy name—neither they nor their kings—by their prostitution and the funeral offerings for their kings at their death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21580L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21580L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When they placed their threshold next to my threshold and their doorposts beside my doorposts, with only a wall between me and them, they defiled my holy name by their detestable practices. So I destroyed them in my anger.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now let them put away from me their prostitution and the funeral offerings for their kings, and I will live among them forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21582M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21582M\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Son of man, describe the temple to the people of Israel, that they may be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21583N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21583N\"></sup> of their sins. Let them consider its perfection,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and if they are ashamed of all they have done, make known to them the design of the temple—its arrangement, its exits and entrances—its whole design and all its regulations and laws. Write these down before them so that they may be faithful to its design and follow all its regulations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21584O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21584O\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“This is the law of the temple: All the surrounding area<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21585P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21585P\"></sup> on top of the mountain will be most holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21585Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21585Q\"></sup> Such is the law of the temple.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“These are the measurements of the altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21586R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21586R\"></sup> in long cubits, that cubit being a cubit and a handbreadth: Its gutter is a cubit deep and a cubit wide, with a rim of one span around the edge. And this is the height of the altar:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>From the gutter on the ground up to the lower ledge that goes around the altar it is two cubits high, and the ledge is a cubit wide. From this lower ledge to the upper ledge that goes around the altar it is four cubits high, and that ledge is also a cubit wide.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Above that, the altar hearth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21588S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21588S\"></sup> is four cubits high, and four horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21588T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21588T\"></sup> project upward from the hearth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The altar hearth is square, twelve cubits long and twelve cubits wide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21589U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21589U\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The upper ledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21590V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21590V\"></sup> also is square, fourteen cubits long and fourteen cubits wide. All around the altar is a gutter of one cubit with a rim of half a cubit. The steps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21590W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21590W\"></sup> of the altar face east.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21590X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21590X\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then he said to me, “Son of man, this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: These will be the regulations for sacrificing burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21591Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21591Y\"></sup> and splashing blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21591Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21591Z\"></sup> against the altar when it is built:",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You are to give a young bull<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21592AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21592AA\"></sup> as a sin offering to the Levitical priests of the family of Zadok,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21592AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21592AB\"></sup> who come near<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21592AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21592AC\"></sup> to minister before me, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You are to take some of its blood and put it on the four horns of the altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21593AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21593AD\"></sup> and on the four corners of the upper ledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21593AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21593AE\"></sup> and all around the rim, and so purify the altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21593AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21593AF\"></sup> and make atonement for it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You are to take the bull for the sin offering and burn it in the designated part of the temple area outside the sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21594AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21594AG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“On the second day you are to offer a male goat without defect for a sin offering, and the altar is to be purified as it was purified with the bull.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When you have finished purifying it, you are to offer a young bull and a ram from the flock, both without defect.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21596AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21596AH\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You are to offer them before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and the priests are to sprinkle salt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21597AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21597AI\"></sup> on them and sacrifice them as a burnt offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“For seven days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21598AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21598AJ\"></sup> you are to provide a male goat daily for a sin offering; you are also to provide a young bull and a ram from the flock, both without defect.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21598AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21598AK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For seven days they are to make atonement for the altar and cleanse it; thus they will dedicate it.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>At the end of these days, from the eighth day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21600AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21600AL\"></sup> on, the priests are to present your burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21600AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21600AM\"></sup> and fellowship offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21600AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21600AN\"></sup> on the altar. Then I will accept you, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>Then the man brought me back to the outer gate of the sanctuary, the one facing east,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21601A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21601A\"></sup> and it was shut.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “This gate is to remain shut. It must not be opened; no one may enter through it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21602B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21602B\"></sup> It is to remain shut because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, has entered through it.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The prince himself is the only one who may sit inside the gateway to eat in the presence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21603C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21603C\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. He is to enter by way of the portico of the gateway and go out the same way.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21603D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21603D\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the man brought me by way of the north gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21604E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21604E\"></sup> to the front of the temple. I looked and saw the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> filling the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21604F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21604F\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I fell facedown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21604G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21604G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Son of man, look carefully, listen closely and give attention to everything I tell you concerning all the regulations and instructions regarding the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Give attention to the entrance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21605H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21605H\"></sup> to the temple and all the exits of the sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21605I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21605I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Say to rebellious Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21606J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21606J\"></sup> ‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Enough of your detestable practices, people of Israel!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In addition to all your other detestable practices, you brought foreigners uncircumcised in heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21607K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21607K\"></sup> and flesh into my sanctuary, desecrating my temple while you offered me food, fat and blood, and you broke my covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21607L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21607L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Instead of carrying out your duty in regard to my holy things, you put others in charge of my sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21608M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21608M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: No foreigner uncircumcised in heart and flesh is to enter my sanctuary, not even the foreigners who live among the Israelites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21609N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21609N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘The Levites who went far from me when Israel went astray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21610O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21610O\"></sup> and who wandered from me after their idols must bear the consequences of their sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21610P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21610P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They may serve in my sanctuary, having charge of the gates of the temple and serving in it; they may slaughter the burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21611Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21611Q\"></sup> and sacrifices for the people and stand before the people and serve them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21611R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21611R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But because they served them in the presence of their idols and made the people of Israel fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21612S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21612S\"></sup> into sin, therefore I have sworn with uplifted hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21612T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21612T\"></sup> that they must bear the consequences of their sin, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21612U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21612U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They are not to come near to serve me as priests or come near any of my holy things or my most holy offerings; they must bear the shame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21613V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21613V\"></sup> of their detestable practices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21613W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21613W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And I will appoint them to guard the temple for all the work that is to be done in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21614X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21614X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“‘But the Levitical priests, who are descendants of Zadok<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21615Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21615Y\"></sup> and who guarded my sanctuary when the Israelites went astray from me, are to come near to minister before me; they are to stand before me to offer sacrifices of fat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21615Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21615Z\"></sup> and blood, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21615AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21615AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They alone are to enter my sanctuary; they alone are to come near my table<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21616AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21616AB\"></sup> to minister before me and serve me as guards.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21616AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21616AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“‘When they enter the gates of the inner court, they are to wear linen clothes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21617AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21617AD\"></sup> they must not wear any woolen garment while ministering at the gates of the inner court or inside the temple.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They are to wear linen turbans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21618AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21618AE\"></sup> on their heads and linen undergarments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21618AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21618AF\"></sup> around their waists. They must not wear anything that makes them perspire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21618AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21618AG\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When they go out into the outer court where the people are, they are to take off the clothes they have been ministering in and are to leave them in the sacred rooms, and put on other clothes, so that the people are not consecrated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21619AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21619AH\"></sup> through contact with their garments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21619AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21619AI\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“‘They must not shave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21620AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21620AJ\"></sup> their heads or let their hair grow long, but they are to keep the hair of their heads trimmed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21620AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21620AK\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>No priest is to drink wine when he enters the inner court.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21621AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21621AL\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>They must not marry widows or divorced women; they may marry only virgins of Israelite descent or widows of priests.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21622AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21622AM\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They are to teach my people the difference between the holy and the common<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21623AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21623AN\"></sup> and show them how to distinguish between the unclean and the clean.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21623AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21623AO\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“‘In any dispute, the priests are to serve as judges<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21624AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21624AP\"></sup> and decide it according to my ordinances. They are to keep my laws and my decrees for all my appointed festivals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21624AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21624AQ\"></sup> and they are to keep my Sabbaths holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21624AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21624AR\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“‘A priest must not defile himself by going near a dead person; however, if the dead person was his father or mother, son or daughter, brother or unmarried sister, then he may defile himself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21625AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21625AS\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>After he is cleansed, he must wait seven days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21626AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21626AT\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>On the day he goes into the inner court of the sanctuary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21627AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21627AU\"></sup> to minister in the sanctuary, he is to offer a sin offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21627AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21627AV\"></sup> for himself, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“‘I am to be the only inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21628AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21628AW\"></sup> the priests have. You are to give them no possession in Israel; I will be their possession.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>They will eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21629AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21629AX\"></sup> the grain offerings, the sin offerings and the guilt offerings; and everything in Israel devoted to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21629AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21629AY\"></sup> will belong to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21629AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21629AZ\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The best of all the firstfruits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21630BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21630BA\"></sup> and of all your special gifts will belong to the priests. You are to give them the first portion of your ground meal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21630BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21630BB\"></sup> so that a blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21630BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21630BC\"></sup> may rest on your household.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21630BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21630BD\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The priests must not eat anything, whether bird or animal, found dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21631BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21631BE\"></sup> or torn by wild animals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21631BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21631BF\"></sup>"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span>“‘When you allot the land as an inheritance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21632A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21632A\"></sup> you are to present to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> a portion of the land as a sacred district, 25,000 cubits long and 20,000 cubits wide; the entire area will be holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21632B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21632B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Of this, a section 500 cubits square<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21633C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21633C\"></sup> is to be for the sanctuary, with 50 cubits around it for open land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In the sacred district, measure off a section 25,000 cubits long and 10,000 cubits wide. In it will be the sanctuary, the Most Holy Place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It will be the sacred portion of the land for the priests,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21635D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21635D\"></sup> who minister in the sanctuary and who draw near to minister before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. It will be a place for their houses as well as a holy place for the sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21635E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21635E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>An area 25,000 cubits long and 10,000 cubits wide will belong to the Levites, who serve in the temple, as their possession for towns to live in.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21636F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21636F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘You are to give the city as its property an area 5,000 cubits wide and 25,000 cubits long, adjoining the sacred portion; it will belong to all Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21637G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21637G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘The prince will have the land bordering each side of the area formed by the sacred district and the property of the city. It will extend westward from the west side and eastward from the east side, running lengthwise from the western to the eastern border parallel to one of the tribal portions.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21638H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21638H\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>This land will be his possession in Israel. And my princes will no longer oppress my people but will allow the people of Israel to possess the land according to their tribes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21639I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21639I\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You have gone far enough, princes of Israel! Give up your violence and oppression<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21640J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21640J\"></sup> and do what is just and right.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21640K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21640K\"></sup> Stop dispossessing my people, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You are to use accurate scales,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21641L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21641L\"></sup> an accurate ephah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21641M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21641M\"></sup> and an accurate bath.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The ephah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21642N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21642N\"></sup> and the bath are to be the same size, the bath containing a tenth of a homer and the ephah a tenth of a homer; the homer is to be the standard measure for both.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The shekel is to consist of twenty gerahs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21643O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21643O\"></sup> Twenty shekels plus twenty-five shekels plus fifteen shekels equal one mina.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘This is the special gift you are to offer: a sixth of an ephah from each homer of wheat and a sixth of an ephah from each homer of barley.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The prescribed portion of olive oil, measured by the bath, is a tenth of a bath from each cor (which consists of ten baths or one homer, for ten baths are equivalent to a homer).",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Also one sheep is to be taken from every flock of two hundred from the well-watered pastures of Israel. These will be used for the grain offerings, burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21646P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21646P\"></sup> and fellowship offerings to make atonement<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21646Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21646Q\"></sup> for the people, declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>All the people of the land will be required to give this special offering to the prince in Israel.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>It will be the duty of the prince to provide the burnt offerings, grain offerings and drink offerings at the festivals, the New Moons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21648R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21648R\"></sup> and the Sabbaths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21648S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21648S\"></sup>—at all the appointed festivals of Israel. He will provide the sin offerings, grain offerings, burnt offerings and fellowship offerings to make atonement for the Israelites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21648T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21648T\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: In the first month<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21649U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21649U\"></sup> on the first day you are to take a young bull without defect<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21649V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21649V\"></sup> and purify the sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21649W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21649W\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The priest is to take some of the blood of the sin offering and put it on the doorposts of the temple, on the four corners of the upper ledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21650X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21650X\"></sup> of the altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21650Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21650Y\"></sup> and on the gateposts of the inner court.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You are to do the same on the seventh day of the month for anyone who sins unintentionally<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21651Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21651Z\"></sup> or through ignorance; so you are to make atonement for the temple.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“‘In the first month on the fourteenth day you are to observe the Passover,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21652AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21652AA\"></sup> a festival lasting seven days, during which you shall eat bread made without yeast.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>On that day the prince is to provide a bull as a sin offering for himself and for all the people of the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21653AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21653AB\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Every day during the seven days of the festival he is to provide seven bulls and seven rams<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21654AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21654AC\"></sup> without defect as a burnt offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and a male goat for a sin offering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21654AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21654AD\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He is to provide as a grain offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21655AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21655AE\"></sup> an ephah for each bull and an ephah for each ram, along with a hin of olive oil for each ephah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21655AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21655AF\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“‘During the seven days of the festival,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21656AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21656AG\"></sup> which begins in the seventh month on the fifteenth day, he is to make the same provision for sin offerings, burnt offerings, grain offerings and oil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21656AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21656AH\"></sup>"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: The gate of the inner court<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21657A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21657A\"></sup> facing east<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21657B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21657B\"></sup> is to be shut on the six working days, but on the Sabbath day and on the day of the New Moon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21657C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21657C\"></sup> it is to be opened.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The prince is to enter from the outside through the portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21658D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21658D\"></sup> of the gateway and stand by the gatepost. The priests are to sacrifice his burnt offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21658E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21658E\"></sup> and his fellowship offerings. He is to bow down in worship at the threshold of the gateway and then go out, but the gate will not be shut until evening.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21658F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21658F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>On the Sabbaths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21659G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21659G\"></sup> and New Moons the people of the land are to worship in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at the entrance of that gateway.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21659H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21659H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The burnt offering the prince brings to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on the Sabbath day is to be six male lambs and a ram, all without defect.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The grain offering given with the ram is to be an ephah, and the grain offering with the lambs is to be as much as he pleases, along with a hin of olive oil for each ephah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21661I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21661I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On the day of the New Moon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21662J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21662J\"></sup> he is to offer a young bull, six lambs and a ram, all without defect.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21662K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21662K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He is to provide as a grain offering one ephah with the bull, one ephah with the ram, and with the lambs as much as he wants to give, along with a hin of oil for each ephah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21663L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21663L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When the prince enters, he is to go in through the portico<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21664M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21664M\"></sup> of the gateway, and he is to come out the same way.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21664N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21664N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘When the people of the land come before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at the appointed festivals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21665O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21665O\"></sup> whoever enters by the north gate to worship is to go out the south gate; and whoever enters by the south gate is to go out the north gate. No one is to return through the gate by which they entered, but each is to go out the opposite gate.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The prince is to be among them, going in when they go in and going out when they go out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21666P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21666P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>At the feasts and the appointed festivals, the grain offering is to be an ephah with a bull, an ephah with a ram, and with the lambs as much as he pleases, along with a hin of oil for each ephah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21667Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21667Q\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“‘When the prince provides<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21668R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21668R\"></sup> a freewill offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21668S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21668S\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—whether a burnt offering or fellowship offerings—the gate facing east is to be opened for him. He shall offer his burnt offering or his fellowship offerings as he does on the Sabbath day. Then he shall go out, and after he has gone out, the gate will be shut.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21668T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21668T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘Every day you are to provide a year-old lamb without defect for a burnt offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; morning by morning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21669U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21669U\"></sup> you shall provide it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21669V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21669V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You are also to provide with it morning by morning a grain offering, consisting of a sixth of an ephah with a third of a hin of oil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21670W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21670W\"></sup> to moisten the flour. The presenting of this grain offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a lasting ordinance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21670X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21670X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So the lamb and the grain offering and the oil shall be provided morning by morning for a regular<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21671Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21671Y\"></sup> burnt offering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21671Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21671Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“‘This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: If the prince makes a gift from his inheritance to one of his sons, it will also belong to his descendants; it is to be their property by inheritance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21672AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21672AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If, however, he makes a gift from his inheritance to one of his servants, the servant may keep it until the year of freedom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21673AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21673AB\"></sup> then it will revert to the prince. His inheritance belongs to his sons only; it is theirs.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The prince must not take<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21674AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21674AC\"></sup> any of the inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21674AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21674AD\"></sup> of the people, driving them off their property. He is to give his sons their inheritance out of his own property, so that not one of my people will be separated from their property.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the man brought me through the entrance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21675AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21675AE\"></sup> at the side of the gate to the sacred rooms facing north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21675AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21675AF\"></sup> which belonged to the priests, and showed me a place at the western end.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He said to me, “This is the place where the priests are to cook the guilt offering and the sin offering and bake the grain offering, to avoid bringing them into the outer court and consecrating<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21676AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21676AG\"></sup> the people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21676AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21676AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He then brought me to the outer court and led me around to its four corners, and I saw in each corner another court.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In the four corners of the outer court were enclosed courts, forty cubits long and thirty cubits wide; each of the courts in the four corners was the same size.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Around the inside of each of the four courts was a ledge of stone, with places for fire built all around under the ledge.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He said to me, “These are the kitchens where those who minister at the temple are to cook the sacrifices of the people.”"
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span>The man brought me back to the entrance to the temple, and I saw water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21681A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21681A\"></sup> coming out from under the threshold of the temple toward the east (for the temple faced east). The water was coming down from under the south side of the temple, south of the altar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21681B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21681B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He then brought me out through the north gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21682C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21682C\"></sup> and led me around the outside to the outer gate facing east, and the water was trickling from the south side.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As the man went eastward with a measuring line<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21683D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21683D\"></sup> in his hand, he measured off a thousand cubits and then led me through water that was ankle-deep.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He measured off another thousand cubits and led me through water that was knee-deep. He measured off another thousand and led me through water that was up to the waist.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He measured off another thousand, but now it was a river<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21685E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21685E\"></sup> that I could not cross, because the water had risen and was deep enough to swim in—a river that no one could cross.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21685F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21685F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He asked me, “Son of man, do you see this?”Then he led me back to the bank of the river.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When I arrived there, I saw a great number of trees on each side of the river.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21687G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21687G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He said to me, “This water flows toward the eastern region and goes down into the Arabah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21688H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21688H\"></sup> where it enters the Dead Sea. When it empties into the sea, the salty water there becomes fresh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21688I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21688I\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Swarms of living creatures will live wherever the river flows. There will be large numbers of fish, because this water flows there and makes the salt water fresh; so where the river flows everything will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21689J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21689J\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Fishermen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21690K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21690K\"></sup> will stand along the shore; from En Gedi<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21690L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21690L\"></sup> to En Eglaim there will be places for spreading nets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21690M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21690M\"></sup> The fish will be of many kinds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21690N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21690N\"></sup>—like the fish of the Mediterranean Sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21690O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21690O\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the swamps and marshes will not become fresh; they will be left for salt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21691P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21691P\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Fruit trees of all kinds will grow on both banks of the river.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21692Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21692Q\"></sup> Their leaves will not wither, nor will their fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21692R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21692R\"></sup> fail. Every month they will bear fruit, because the water from the sanctuary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21692S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21692S\"></sup> flows to them. Their fruit will serve for food and their leaves for healing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21692T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21692T\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “These are the boundaries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21693U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21693U\"></sup> of the land that you will divide among the twelve tribes of Israel as their inheritance, with two portions for Joseph.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21693V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21693V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You are to divide it equally among them. Because I swore with uplifted hand to give it to your ancestors, this land will become your inheritance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21694W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21694W\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“This is to be the boundary of the land:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21695X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21695X\"></sup>“On the north side it will run from the Mediterranean Sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21695Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21695Y\"></sup> by the Hethlon road<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21695Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21695Z\"></sup> past Lebo Hamath to Zedad,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Berothah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21696AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21696AA\"></sup> and Sibraim (which lies on the border between Damascus and Hamath),<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21696AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21696AB\"></sup> as far as Hazer Hattikon, which is on the border of Hauran.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The boundary will extend from the sea to Hazar Enan, along the northern border of Damascus, with the border of Hamath to the north. This will be the northern boundary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21697AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21697AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“On the east side the boundary will run between Hauran and Damascus, along the Jordan between Gilead and the land of Israel, to the Dead Sea and as far as Tamar. This will be the eastern boundary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21698AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21698AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“On the south side it will run from Tamar as far as the waters of Meribah Kadesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21699AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21699AE\"></sup> then along the Wadi of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21699AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21699AF\"></sup> to the Mediterranean Sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21699AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21699AG\"></sup> This will be the southern boundary.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“On the west side, the Mediterranean Sea will be the boundary to a point opposite Lebo Hamath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21700AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21700AH\"></sup> This will be the western boundary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21700AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21700AI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“You are to distribute this land among yourselves according to the tribes of Israel.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You are to allot it as an inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21702AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21702AJ\"></sup> for yourselves and for the foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21702AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21702AK\"></sup> residing among you and who have children. You are to consider them as native-born Israelites; along with you they are to be allotted an inheritance among the tribes of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21702AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21702AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In whatever tribe a foreigner resides, there you are to give them their inheritance,” declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21703AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21703AM\"></sup>"
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span>“These are the tribes, listed by name: At the northern frontier, Dan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21704A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21704A\"></sup> will have one portion; it will follow the Hethlon road<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21704B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21704B\"></sup> to Lebo Hamath;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21704C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21704C\"></sup> Hazar Enan and the northern border of Damascus next to Hamath will be part of its border from the east side to the west side.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Asher<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21705D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21705D\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Dan from east to west.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Naphtali<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21706E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21706E\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Asher from east to west.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Manasseh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21707F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21707F\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Naphtali from east to west.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Ephraim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21708G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21708G\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Manasseh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21708H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21708H\"></sup> from east to west.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21708I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21708I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Reuben<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21709J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21709J\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Ephraim from east to west.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21710K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21710K\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Reuben from east to west.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Bordering the territory of Judah from east to west will be the portion you are to present as a special gift. It will be 25,000 cubits wide, and its length from east to west will equal one of the tribal portions; the sanctuary will be in the center of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21711L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21711L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The special portion you are to offer to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be 25,000 cubits long and 10,000 cubits wide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21712M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21712M\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This will be the sacred portion for the priests. It will be 25,000 cubits long on the north side, 10,000 cubits wide on the west side, 10,000 cubits wide on the east side and 25,000 cubits long on the south side. In the center of it will be the sanctuary of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21713N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21713N\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This will be for the consecrated priests, the Zadokites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21714O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21714O\"></sup> who were faithful in serving me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21714P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21714P\"></sup> and did not go astray as the Levites did when the Israelites went astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21714Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21714Q\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It will be a special gift to them from the sacred portion of the land, a most holy portion, bordering the territory of the Levites.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Alongside the territory of the priests, the Levites will have an allotment 25,000 cubits long and 10,000 cubits wide. Its total length will be 25,000 cubits and its width 10,000 cubits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21716R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21716R\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They must not sell or exchange any of it. This is the best of the land and must not pass into other hands, because it is holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21717S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21717S\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“The remaining area, 5,000 cubits wide and 25,000 cubits long, will be for the common use of the city, for houses and for pastureland. The city will be in the center of it",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and will have these measurements: the north side 4,500 cubits, the south side 4,500 cubits, the east side 4,500 cubits, and the west side 4,500 cubits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21719T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21719T\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The pastureland for the city will be 250 cubits on the north, 250 cubits on the south, 250 cubits on the east, and 250 cubits on the west.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>What remains of the area, bordering on the sacred portion and running the length of it, will be 10,000 cubits on the east side and 10,000 cubits on the west side. Its produce will supply food for the workers of the city.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21721U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21721U\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The workers from the city who farm it will come from all the tribes of Israel.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The entire portion will be a square, 25,000 cubits on each side. As a special gift you will set aside the sacred portion, along with the property of the city.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“What remains on both sides of the area formed by the sacred portion and the property of the city will belong to the prince. It will extend eastward from the 25,000 cubits of the sacred portion to the eastern border, and westward from the 25,000 cubits to the western border. Both these areas running the length of the tribal portions will belong to the prince, and the sacred portion with the temple sanctuary will be in the center of them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21724V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21724V\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So the property of the Levites and the property of the city will lie in the center of the area that belongs to the prince. The area belonging to the prince will lie between the border of Judah and the border of Benjamin.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“As for the rest of the tribes: Benjamin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21726W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21726W\"></sup> will have one portion; it will extend from the east side to the west side.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Simeon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21727X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21727X\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Benjamin from east to west.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Issachar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21728Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21728Y\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Simeon from east to west.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Zebulun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21729Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21729Z\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Issachar from east to west.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Gad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21730AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21730AA\"></sup> will have one portion; it will border the territory of Zebulun from east to west.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“The southern boundary of Gad will run south from Tamar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21731AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21731AB\"></sup> to the waters of Meribah Kadesh, then along the Wadi of Egypt to the Mediterranean Sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21731AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21731AC\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“This is the land you are to allot as an inheritance to the tribes of Israel, and these will be their portions,” declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21732AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21732AD\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“These will be the exits of the city: Beginning on the north side, which is 4,500 cubits long,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>the gates of the city will be named after the tribes of Israel. The three gates on the north side will be the gate of Reuben, the gate of Judah and the gate of Levi.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“On the east side, which is 4,500 cubits long, will be three gates: the gate of Joseph, the gate of Benjamin and the gate of Dan.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“On the south side, which measures 4,500 cubits, will be three gates: the gate of Simeon, the gate of Issachar and the gate of Zebulun.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“On the west side, which is 4,500 cubits long, will be three gates: the gate of Gad, the gate of Asher and the gate of Naphtali.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21737AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21737AE\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“The distance all around will be 18,000 cubits.“And the name of the city from that time on will be:<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the Lord is there</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-21738AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-21738AF\"></sup>”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;